(6, 27, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/mypath%20banner.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=My+Path+Sdn+Bhd+Bayan+Lepas+Penang&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=my+path&amp;sll=4.18646,109.48935&amp;sspn=13.315439,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=My+Path+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Bayan+Lepas,+Penang&amp;t=m&amp;cid=5822681217917641387&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our passion at MyPath is to see graduates start right in their career journey. We believed our working experience with the industries, knowing employers today&rsquo;s need in hiring, understanding global business trend and working with youth organizations, we are able to value-add to your undergraduates.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt; padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #333333;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/mypath1.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="340" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.383333206176758px;">We have series of workshops designed with today&rsquo;s industrial expectation and latest global hiring trends. &nbsp;We believed we will be the right organization to share with your students because we currently represent the industries from Small-Medium (SMI/SME) to Multi National (MNC) across wide specializations. &nbsp;We are able to share the insight from a Headhunter point of view on practical tips, do and don&rsquo;t of applying to the Multi-Nationals &amp; Small-Medium Industries.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">If you&rsquo;re looking for practical information and up-to-date knowledge to equip and develop your undergraduate,&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Contact US TODAY! We are happy to share.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br /></span></p>', '<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/mypath2.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="300" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/mypath3.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="330" /></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: .25in; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333;">&ldquo;There was one individual who walked about 20 min from his campus dorm to see me at my Video-Resume Recording room and asked me about the D&rsquo;Graduate competition whether it is going to be in English.&nbsp; I told him yes it is because that will be the common language used in business world. He told me then that he wanted to withdraw his participation because he cannot speak English. I was puzzled when he said that because till that moment, his whole conversation with me was actually in English and I didn&rsquo;t see any problem in his English conversation. It was clear and direct.</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333;">I then told him, your English is not your issue, let me help you with the video-resume and I will be patient to help you till you get it right.</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333;">He paused for a while and then said OK.&nbsp;&nbsp; He told me his dream was to be a broadcaster/host like &ldquo;Nawi&rdquo; ( I thought that must have been the Astro-Annum talk show guy)&nbsp; I replied, why not, anything is possible when you pursue with your heart. He then agree to record his video.</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333;">When I started my recording, he became so alive and spoke so well with just 3 mins self-introduction. To my amazement, he did better than others who came to record with Excellent English. Some even had to record their videos at least 15 times before they got them right.</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.25in; line-height: 11.55pt;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333;">He only has to do 3 takes and he was perfect.&nbsp; I thought to myself, what actually is not right with him? He has it but he didn&rsquo;t know he has got it. When I played the video back to him, he was so happy and you can see he started realizing his talent (just need practice and refinement). Immediately after the 15 mins spent with him, he gained his confidence and told me that he believed he can now do it. I told him, yes, the evidence was clear to see.&nbsp; To me, he transformed in 15 min. and that was &ldquo;WOW&rdquo; for me.</span></em></p>', 'http://www.mypath.com.my/index.php', 1, 0, 9, 815, '2012-09-22 11:04:55', '2012-12-21 10:10:11'),
(7, 2642, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Eastern+Pretech+(Malaysia)+Sdn+Bhd+Taman+Sungai+Besi+Kuala+Lumpur+Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=eastern+pre&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.671539,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Eastern+Pretech+(Malaysia)+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Taman+Sungai+Besi,+Kuala+Lumpur,+Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur&amp;t=m&amp;cid=15500414661524775746&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, Swiss, SunSans-Regular; font-size: small; text-align: justify; color: #888888;">Eastern Pretech has, over the past two decades, acquired invaluable construction know-how and experience by combining good local construction practice with strong technological back-up from leading international specialists. This allows us to lead the construction industry with innovative solutions to our clients'' satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; text-align: justify; color: #888888;">We believe that innovative, industrially produced construction solutions will further continue their breakthrough in Malaysia. Together with our strong local know-how and international background, Eastern Pretech will be an important contributor in the development as the country gears itself towards the attainment of Vision 2020.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; text-align: justify;"><br /></span></p>', '<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/gallery1(2).jpg" alt="" width="430" height="300" /></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #0000ff;">Life In The Group</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">With more than forty years'' practice as an equal opportunity employer operating in a multi-cultural society, NSL invests in people. It recognises and rewards talent, loyalty and entrepreneurship, providing a varied work experience through multi-industry &amp; multinational operations.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/testimonial(1).jpg" alt="" width="404" height="166" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f;">More importantly, it nurtures the spirit of innovation through a corporate culture emphasizing excellence through technology &amp; lifelong learning.</span><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: blue; font-size: 11pt;">Training</span><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f;">NSL believes that lifelong learning begins with training, to continually adapt its people to the changing work environment and new technologies -- and add new, creative ways to think out of the box.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f;"><br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: #7f7f7f;">After orientation, new employees undergo structured on-the-job training to gain an understanding of their jobs, and are then put on a continual job-specific training programme, reviewed annually to ensure that goals for professional and career development are on track.</span><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'http://www.epmsb.com.my/index.html', 1, 1, 1, 1134, '2012-10-30 12:25:51', '2015-08-04 11:19:51'),
(8, 395, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/HMScover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No.+15-6,+The+Boulevard,+Mid+Valley+City,+Lingkaran+Syed+Putra,+59200+Kuala+Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;aq=&amp;sll=3.118876,101.678563&amp;sspn=0.006139,0.009645&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Lingkaran+Syed+Putra,+Mid+Valley+City,+59200+Kuala+Lumpur,+Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/training%20course.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="150" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">My core interest in business is to provide aviation manpower preparatory training and placement services. To gain more knowledge and experience, I worked for many years at an aviation manpower preparatory training providing company.<br /> </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">There is where and when I discovered my following strengths and abilities.<br /> <!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br /> <!--[endif]--></span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;">Initiate      contact, secure recruitment job orders, organizing interviews and      maintaining a professional working relationship with many reputable      international airlines in Asia and Middle East such as Air Asia, Etihad      Airways, Oman Air, Royal Jordanian, Kuwait Airways, Gulf Air, Sudan      Airways, FireFly, Tiger Airways, JetStar Asia just to name a few.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;">Successfully networked and      sourced suitably qualified candidates for Flight Attendant and selected      ground handling positions in Asia, Far East, Middle East and Eastern      Europe for the above mentioned airlines.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Although the required minimum targeted number of suitably qualified      candidates for interviews was met, the percentage of rejection or failure      rate was very high and it is the same at any airline interview in the      world. Many of the candidates who failed were either not familiar with the      interview process, not having the required level of English Language      proficiency or simply just not prepared. Surprisingly, a large number of      them have acquired initial interview preparatory training.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HMS%20office.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HMS%20Etihad.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/silkair.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="310" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #888888;">"HMS has put together a team of carefully selected seasoned expert trainers consisting of former Flight Attendant Chief Trainers and Recruiters from reputable international airlines, where trainees get second to none coaching on how to pass the rigorous flight attendant recruitment process"</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 150px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/MAS%20photo.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="310" /></p>', 'http://www.hmsmalaysia.com/index.php', 0, 0, 6, 1184, '2012-10-30 17:15:18', '2013-01-26 17:45:22'),
(9, 381, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/cover%20ensurepotential.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=50450+Jalan+Pinang+Kuala+Lumpur+Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Jalan+Pinang,50450,Kuala+Lumpur.&amp;sll=3.152707,101.712155&amp;sspn=0.012277,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Pinang,+50450+Kuala+Lumpur,+Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><strong style="color: #414042; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;">EPSB</strong><span style="color: #414042; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;is a leading Financial Trading research provider &amp; Institute of Financial Science with the primary focus on Research &amp; development of financial trading technologies &amp; methodologies to individual traders, brokers and sub-broker in Financial Markets. Our Advisory services cover Precious Metals &amp; other Financial products</span><span class="ecx" style="font-size: small; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana; color: #ffffff;"><span class="ecx" style="line-height: 17px; border-collapse: collapse;">.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><span class="ecx" style="font-size: small; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana; color: #ffffff;"><span class="ecx" style="line-height: 17px; border-collapse: collapse;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/ensurepotential1.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="250" /><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="ecx" style="font-size: small; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana; color: #ffffff;"><span class="ecx" style="line-height: 17px; border-collapse: collapse;"><strong style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">Mission centers on T.E.A.C.H :</strong><br style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;" /><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">&gt; To Train every man on the street to use our proven Trading Systems.</span><br style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;" /><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">&gt; To Enlighten Traders on Successful Trading = Knowing Yourself.</span><br style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;" /><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">&gt; To Advocate responsible Trading habits to every trader.</span><br style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;" /><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">&gt; To Create a continuous learning environment for Traders.</span><br style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;" /><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px;">&gt; To Help the needy through the newly created Wealth.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">Our team is a group of highly professional traders with many years of&nbsp; trading experience. We trade for multinationals, financial institutions, banks, brokers and money managers.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/platform.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="230" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">With the help of our credible service, we''ll show you how to make a lucrative living from trading.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">After you subscribe, you''ll quickly realise our accuracy, expertise and years of experience is worth the investment.</span><br /><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">Because your success is ours - and we do not like to fail/</span><br /><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">It''s why we are the only signal provider that has never suffered a negative trading month. Nothing beats our performance.</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">EPSB is widely considered the world standard in the&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">stock charting</strong><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">technical analysis tool</strong><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;industry &ndash; a position that it has held since its inception in 2007. EPSB flagship products most people recognize&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><br style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;" /><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/testimonial(2).jpg" alt="" width="225" height="150" /><br style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">Like other top software companies, EPSB cannot sit still. Always improving, evolving and progressing, EPSB is continually on the lookout for&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">goal-oriented, hard working, responsible people</strong><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;to join its workforce.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;" /><br style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;" /><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">EPSB offers chosen candidates&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">competitive wages, a pleasant working environment, and excellent benefits, including medical, dental, and vision</strong><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;" /><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">Please take a moment to look over our currently available positions and consider the possibility of&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">joining the EPSB team</strong><span style="color: #525253; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">.</span></p>', 'http://www.ensurepotential.com', 0, 0, 9, 664, '2012-11-04 13:33:34', '2013-01-26 17:45:50'),
(10, 433, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/kraftfoodcover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kraft+Malaysia+Sdn.+Bhd.+%40+First+Avenue+Dataran+Bandar+Utama+Bandar+Utama+Petaling+Jaya+Selangor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=kraft&amp;sll=3.146708,101.617023&amp;sspn=0.006138,0.009645&amp;g=1+First+Avenue,+2A,+DAtaran+Bandar+Utama,+Bandar+Utama+Damansara,+47800+Petaling+Jaya,+Selangor&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Kraft+Malaysia+Sdn.+Bhd.+%40+First+Avenue&amp;hnear=Dataran+Bandar+Utama,+Bandar+Utama,+47800+Petaling+Jaya,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; color: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;">People and Diversity</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 18.85pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">We''re open and inclusive. It''s a simple concept. Being open and inclusive is critical to creating a delicious work experience for our employees and business partners. And it''s the foundation of our strategy to build a high-performing culture.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<strong><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; color: #333333;">Mixing in Wellness</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Healthy employees are engaged and productive. So it''s no surprise that to grow a successful business</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6.25pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">you need a healthy workforce. That''s why we encourage and support our employees in having healthier lifestyles. We offer various health and well-being tools and resources in many of the facilities we have around the world &ndash; and our goal is to expand these efforts each year. Though the current tools and resources may differ based on local and cultural needs, they generally offer similar elements around nutritional, physical and mental well-being. Here are just a few ways we''re helping our employees feel better&ndash;physically and mentally:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 15.15pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">Lifestyle improvement programs, such as stress management, weight management and smoking cessation</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 15.15pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">Fitness and/or sports facilities onsite, incentives for gym membership reimbursement and employee sports competitions</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 15.15pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">Health screenings and exams, including vaccinations and flu shots</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 15.15pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">Healthier options and nutrition information in our cafeterias and canteens</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 15.15pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt;">Health newsletters/intranet sites that offer health tips and work-life/flex time programs.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; color: #333333;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We are also an active member of the World Economic Forum''s&nbsp;<a href="http://alliance.weforum.org/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #4f2170; text-decoration: none;">Workplace Wellness Alliance</span></a>. The Alliance brings together 39 multinational companies from around the world that are committed to advancing wellness in the workplace by improving the overall health and wellbeing of the global workforce</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6.25pt; line-height: 13.75pt;"><span style="mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; color: #333333;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></span></p>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/kraftgallery1.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" /></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Segoe UI'', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.983333587646484px;">Every day, our success depends upon 100,000 capable, dedicated and diverse MondelÄ“z International employees around the world. Treating them well and providing them with a workplace that is safe is the right thing to do and essential for our long-term success.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Segoe UI'', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.983333587646484px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/krafttestimonial.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="234" /><br /></span></p>', 'www.kraftfoodscompany.com', 1, 0, 8, 1804, '2012-11-10 14:06:45', '2013-02-14 13:28:45'),
(11, 445, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/seagatecover.jpg', 'http://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Seagate+Kampung+Jawa+Highway+Bayan+Baru+Penang&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=peang+seagate&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.671539,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Seagate&amp;hnear=Kampung+Jawa+Hwy,+11900+Bayan+Lepas,+Penang&amp;t=m&amp;cid=3390590280736170666&amp;z=13&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-size: 21px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Our Values</h3>\r\n<div class="textColumns clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: url(http://www.seagate.com/ww/images/global/bg/sep_text_col.gif); color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px; background-position: 196px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;">\r\n<div class="col" style="margin: 0px 16px 0px 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; float: left; width: 190px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px;">One Billion and Beyond</h3>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 20px;">In 2008, Seagate became the first hard drive manufacturer to ship one billion drives. This incredible milestone was followed by innovations such as our first solid state drives and solid state hybrid drives, the first 1TB per disc capacity point and the industry&rsquo;s thinnest 2.5 inch hard drive.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col" style="margin: 0px 16px 0px 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; float: left; width: 190px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px;">Cloudy with a Chance of Storage</h3>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 20px;">Seagate is the worldwide leader in storage solutions for cloud computing, and our Unified Storage architecture aligns with this shift towards more flexible, lower cost computing. Developed over three decades of enterprise storage leadership, Unified Storage is an approach that delivers powerful yet simple enterprise-class storage solutions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col omega" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; float: left; width: 190px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px;">Store, Share, Enjoy</h3>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 20px;">Seagate solutions are not just for businesses and system builders. Innovations such as our Backup Plus family of products help everyone who wants to store, share and safeguard their most precious digital assets. Through technology leadership and innovation, Seagate helps businesses and individuals maximise the potential of their digital content in an on-demand world.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/gpY8c7lT_7k?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/gpY8c7lT_7k?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/Kss98VdhSj0?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/Kss98VdhSj0?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', 'www.seagate.com', 1, 0, 19, 5024, '2012-11-12 15:37:42', '2013-07-01 16:14:21'),
(12, 4897, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/sushikin.jpg', 'http://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jalan+Subang+5,+Taman+Perindustrian+Subang,+47610,+Subang+Jaya,+Selangor.&amp;aq=&amp;sll=3.080759,101.584289&amp;sspn=0.006128,0.009645&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Subang+5,+Taman+Perindustrian+Subang,+47630+Subang+Jaya,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">The novelty, affordability and efficiency of Sushi King restaurants proved to be our distinctive advantage; our specially equipped sushi-making machines and conveyor system showcasing quality sushi in a hygienic environment, as we offer quick and fresh food to suit today&rsquo;s fast pace of life. The unique experience of selecting from a variety of sushi dishes on the revolving conveyor belt at leisure has attracted a wide variety of customers from all walks of life, from Japanese tourists and expatriates to even those initially unfamiliar with Japanese cuisine.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Today, we have expanded our expertise to include specialised catering services for a variety of events and functions. As we continue to grow, we set our sights on further regional and eventually international expansion.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sushiking1.jpg" alt="" width="244" height="342" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/article/sushikingmap.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sushiking2.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="400" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sushiking3.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="400" /></p>', '<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/OIoc_4A6boY?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="data" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/OIoc_4A6boY?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/OIoc_4A6boY?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" />\r\n<param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', 'http://www.sushi-king.com/index.php', 1, 0, 16, 1400, '2012-11-12 16:16:22', '2015-06-11 03:42:34'),
(13, 438, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/honeywellcover.jpg', 'http://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Honeywell+Aerospace+Avionics+Malaysia+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=hone&amp;sll=5.360002,100.39752&amp;sspn=0.04888,0.077162&amp;g=Kawasan+Perusahaan+Bebas+Prai,+13600+Prai,+Pulau+Pinang,+Malaysia&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;cid=15031003939941710525&amp;hq=Honeywell+Aerospace+Avionics+Malaysia+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: #3375aa;">The Five Initiatives</h2>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><img style="border-style: none; outline: none;" src="http://www.careersathoneywell.com/Portals/0/The5Initiatives.jpg" alt="" align="left" />To succeed in your Honeywell career, you''ll need to understand and appreciate the critical role of our Five Initiatives &ndash; Growth, Productivity, Cash, People and the Enablers.</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: #3375aa;">Growth</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">Honeywell''s objective is to achieve profitable growth with emphasis on organic or internal growth, using four pillars of organic growth. The pillars include doing a superb job for our customers every day; superior sales and marketing organization; globalization; and robust, funded technology roadmaps for new products and services.</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: #3375aa;">Productivity</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">Honeywell has an outstanding track record in driving continuous improvement in support of improved Productivity. We will maintain that level of performance, even as we increase our emphasis on Growth.</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: #3375aa;">Cash</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">This initiative focuses on driving improvements in working capital, payables, receivables and inventory. Cash is the lifeblood of any business. As we increase cash flow, we can take advantage of opportunities to reinvest in our businesses through strategic acquisitions, technology roadmaps and stock buybacks. The positive impact on employees and shareowners alike is huge.</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: #3375aa;">People</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">From the Boardroom to the manufacturing floor, we focus on having the best people organized the right way, and motivated. At Honeywell, employees are given opportunities to learn, grow, and develop and they are rewarded for their contributions. Our size, the industries we serve, and the breadth of our portfolio enable people to have dynamic careers, develop into leaders, and gain experiences across businesses, functions, and regions.</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: #3375aa;">Enablers</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">Our three Enablers&mdash;The Honeywell Operating System (HOS), Functional Transformation (FT), and Velocity Product Development&trade; (VPD)&mdash;are internal business processes driving efficiency and service quality, bringing world-class products and services to market faster and more cost-effectively for our customers. The Honeywell Operating System drives sustainable improvements in our manufacturing operations to generate exceptional performance in safety, quality, delivery, cost, and inventory management. Functional Transformation is HOS for our administrative functions&mdash;Finance, Legal, HR, IT and Purchasing&mdash;standardizing the way we work, reducing costs and improving service quality.</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;">Velocity Product Development (VPD) strengthens our new product development process.</p>', '<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/F7UBlqQfex0?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/F7UBlqQfex0?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB&amp;rel=0" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px; color: #3375aa;">Benefits at Honeywell</h2>\r\n<p><img style="border-style: none; outline: none;" src="http://www.careersathoneywell.com/Portals/0/BenefitsatHoneywell40.jpg" alt="" align="left" /><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Honeywell counts on our people to deliver superb performance for our customers every day &ndash; and in return, we offer compensation that links your pay directly to business and individual results. Our pay-for-performance approach is designed to be fair and consistent, individually differentiated based on results, market competitive and compliant with local laws.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We also provide competitive benefits programs in every region in which we do business. While our benefits plans vary in availability in our different locations, we offer a broad range of benefits that are part of the value you receive as a Honeywell employee. Wherever you are with us, you will find benefits that can help ensure your health and well being, and contribute to your financial security.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #3375aa; font-size: 18px; line-height: 20px;">Learning &amp; Development</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><img style="border-style: none; outline: none;" src="http://www.careersathoneywell.com/Portals/0/LearningandDevelopment.jpg" alt="" align="left" /><span style="font-size: 10pt;">At Honeywell, continuous learning and leadership development are fundamental to how we consistently lead, innovate and grow. We are committed to the constant improvement of our people as well as our processes &ndash; and we offer a broad range of tools, programs and curricula to help employees prepare and execute their development plans.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our global&nbsp;<strong>Learning Management System</strong>&nbsp;enables you to identify opportunities to develop skills for your current role, as well as acquire new skills and knowledge to prepare you for future challenges and roles within Honeywell.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Honeywell&rsquo;s&nbsp;<strong>Talent Management</strong>&nbsp;framework includes frequent dialogue and in-depth reviews among leaders, managers and employees. This process helps identify your current strengths, areas needing improvement, and potential future positions within Honeywell. While working with your leader to set annual goals that align with our&nbsp;<a style="border: none; outline: none; text-decoration: initial; color: #3375aa;" href="http://www.careersathoneywell.com/en/WorkingatHoneywell.aspx?tid=1"><strong>Five Initiatives</strong></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a style="border: none; outline: none; text-decoration: initial; color: #3375aa;" href="http://www.careersathoneywell.com/en/WorkingatHoneywell.aspx?tid=2"><strong>Twelve Behaviors</strong></a>, you&rsquo;ll also identify development opportunities that may include experiences on the job, relationships with peers and managers, stretch assignments, classroom learning, and eLearning.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our&nbsp;<strong>Honeywell Performance and Development</strong>&nbsp;process enables leaders to align your individual objectives to business goals; assess your performance in terms of results and our Twelve Behaviors; develop action plans to support your current and future success; and provide candid feedback to help you grow.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 5px 0px; margin: 6px 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Honeywell&rsquo;s compensation philosophy is performance-based, so understanding the relationship between your goals, performance and results will be a critical component to your success with us.</span></p>', 'http://honeywell.com/Pages/Home.aspx', 1, 0, 11, 2784, '2012-11-12 16:53:37', '2013-03-10 14:41:11');
