(22, 14, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/VS%20Industry%20cover.jpg', 'http://maps.google.com.my/maps?source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=PTD86556,+Jalan+Murni+12,+Murni+Industrial+Estate&amp;sll=4.18646,109.48935&amp;sspn=13.315439,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=PTD86556,+Jalan+Murni+12,+Murni+Industrial+Estate&amp;hnear=Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=1301607125725689946&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><strong style="font-size: 11pt;">Why join us:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">At VS we are committed to providing a fulfilling workplace for our employees to grow further by providing conducive working environment, benefits &amp; remunerations. Some of our benefits &amp; remunerations includes:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Free medical &amp; dental treatment</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Free insurance coverage</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Free uniform</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Facilities like canteen, in-house clinic, ATM</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Comprehensive staff training</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Performance bonus</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Yearly salary increment</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Salary adjustment upon confirmation</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&bull;<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Attractive allowance for oversea and travelling</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Core Advantages:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style