(23, 526, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/GES%20Manufacturing%20Cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Ges+Manufacturing+Services+(M)+Sdn.+Bhd.+Jalan+Persiaran+Selasih+Senai+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=GES+man&amp;sll=4.18646,109.48935&amp;sspn=13.315439,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Ges+Manufacturing+Services+(M)+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=Jalan+Persiaran+Selasih,+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Senai+3,+81400+Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;"><span style="line-height: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;">GES Manufacturing Services (M) Sdn Bhd, a member of Venture Group of Companies.In its pursuit to create unparalleled enterprise excellence across design and engineering, manufacturing and distribution, Venture has forged numerous meaningful partnerships and alliances. As it assumes a key role in the enterprise chain, Venture will continue to tap the knowledge and best-in-class capabilities of global enterprises for breakthrough innovations.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/venture_office.jpg" alt="" width="278" height="202" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>The Power Of Shared Values</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">At Venture, we work as a closely-knit team with a shared value system, where seeking to realise the corporate vision and achieve personal fulfillment, is an everyday pursuit.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Our core values are essential enduring principles that guide every Venture staff, by way of our policies, practices and goals. These deep-rooted internal values will overtime, shape our attitude towards our work and direct us in the way we behave and work with our colleagues, customers and business partners.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">We believe our core values will steer us to the best path for achieving our desired goals, both individually and as a team.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Venture (SGX: VENM.SI) was founded in 1984 as a global electronics services provider. Today, it is a leading global provider of technology services, products and solutions with established capabilities spanning marketing research, design and development, product and process engineering, design for manufacturability, supply chain management, as well as product refurbishment and technical support across a range of high-mix, high-value and complex products.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/venture%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="553" height="154" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 16px;">Venture''s efforts to achieve world-class excellence in all aspects of its business has been recognised both by our customers and the financial media. These string of accolades not only testify to our commitment to deliver above and beyond our customers'' expectations, but are also proof of our innovative spirit, our high standards of corporate governance and corporate management. This is evident that we have more than just the basic fundamentals. We have what it takes to be at the cutting-edge of the industry.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/venture%20customer%20recognitions.jpg" alt="" width="228" height="119" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Customer Recognitions</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 9pt;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">HP: Successful support for Retail Publishing Solutions (2011)</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Avago: For excellent outsourcing support (2011)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">IBM: Supplier Recognition for IBM''s Tape Storage Business (2008)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Intel: Embedded and Communications Alliance Membership (2008)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">NCR: Supplier of the Year (2008)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">HP: Recognition for the Development and Completion of the HP Officejet H470 Mobile Printer (2008)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Agilent: Quality Award (2007)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Fluke: Outstanding Supplier Partnership (2007)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">HP: Excellent Operational Support (2007)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Intel Asia: Best ODM in Designing Wireless Handheld Device (2005)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Intermec: Supplier of the Year (2005)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Agilent: Supplier of the Year (2004, 2005)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Coherent: Quality Workmanship Award (2004)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">HP Imaging &amp; Printing Group: For outstanding performance and delivery (2004)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Iomega: Supplier of the Year (2003)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">HP Personal LaserJet Solutions: For excellent NPI support by (2003)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">HP Spain: For outstanding performance (2003)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">IBM Japan: Excellent supplier (2002)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Lexar: For excellent service provided (2002)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Xerox: For excellent execution and delivery (2002)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 16px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; fo