white-space: pre;"> </span> </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">For Melaka positions:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">General Manager,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">Administration Division,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">Honda Malaysia Sdn. Bhd.,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">Hicom Industrial Park Pegoh,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">P.O Box. 70,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">78000 Alor Gajah, Melaka.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">Email: <a href="mailto:recruitment@honda.net.my" target="_blank">recruitment@honda.net.my</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">2. Online</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #666699;">Just click on the job you''re interested in and fill in the online application form.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.honda.com.my/', 1, 1, 28, 6978, '2013-04-01 15:33:48', '2015-07-28 12:14:41'),
