(29, 865, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/prent%20cover.jpg', 'http://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Prent+(M)+Sdn+Bhd+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Senai+Fasa+3+Senai+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=prent&amp;sll=1.544872,103.696727&amp;sspn=0.209007,0.308647&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Prent+(M)+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Kawasan+Perindustrian+Senai+Fasa+3,+Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=7657283950853703922&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">At Prent, we understand our customers&rsquo; sustainability and cost-saving challenges&mdash;both in the marketplace and within their own internal operations.</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Prent%20factories.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We are committed to &ldquo;Design More with Less&rdquo; and helping our customers meet their sustainability goals. We encourage customers to evaluate their existing products and let us know if they are interested in alternate materials. Very often we can help minimize costs and add sustainability in new ways.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our superior design process provides customers with packages that optimize functional performance, minimize material usage, reduce costs and meet new standards.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We are committed to the development and pre-qualification of new materials and processes to support customer needs. Through extensive R&amp;D efforts&mdash;and our partnership with GOEX Corporation&mdash;we&rsquo;re helping customers identify acceptable and/or environmentally friendly new materials (where appropriate) such as:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Prent%20environmental.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Closed-loop recycling (recycling of customer scrap into functionally re-usable material)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Use of commercially available compostable and bio-based materials</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We use Prent Returnable Containers to enhance product protection and improve freight efficiencies by eliminating wood skids and related corrugate packing materials. Returnable Containers offer customers many advantages, including:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Durable, clean packing</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Increased part protection</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Warehouse optimization, since Containers are stackable without the need for racks</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Closed loop packing, since Containers are easily collapsible for return shipment</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Reduced freight costs by densifying truck trailer capacity</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Prent Malaysia is ISO 14001 certified for environmental management systems.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">All Prent packaging and packaging processes are RoHS compliant and contain no lead, mercury, cadmium, hexavalent chromium, polybrominated biphenyls or polybrominated diphenyl ethers.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Copyright (c) <a href="http://www.123rf.com">123RF Stock Photos</a></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/prent%20Malaysia%20facility.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="290" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Prent%20gallery2.jpg" alt="" width="569" height="401" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/prent%20gallery3.jpg" alt="" width="569" height="401" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/prent%20gallery4.jpg" alt="" width="569" height="320" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Prent%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="569" height="401" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Source: Prent.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Be prepared to discuss your skills, experience, strengths, accomplishments, goals and job expectations. Get to know Prent Corporation by reviewing the materials on our website. During the interview, let us know why you would be the best person for the job.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="font-size: 10pt; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Prent%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="180" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Source: Prent.com</p>', 'http://www.prent.com/', 1, 0, 17, 1745, '2013-05-14 16:12:27', '2013-09-21 13:35:25'),
