(37, 745, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/EEW%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jalan+Tengah+81700+Pasir+Gudang+Malaysia&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.579085,104.127045&amp;sspn=0.785218,1.234589&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Tengah,+81750+Masai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<h2 style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: #e2001a; font-family: Arial, verdana, tahoma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;">EEW Quality renders success and satisfied clients</h2>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888; font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 16px;">Your competent partner for carbon pipes, low alloy pipes, stainless steel pipes and clad pipes as well as pre-fabrication of piping components.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; line-height: 16px;">EEW makes no compromise where material, workmanship and quality control&nbsp;are concerned. Our quality is guaranteed by observing exactly manufacturing and quality control procedures as well as the rules of our quality management system.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva;">EEW is entitled to use the API 5L, 5LC, 5LD and 2B monograms. Numerous national and international certifications prove the high level of quality.</span></p>\r\n<p class="bodytext" style="margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: #6c6c6c; font-family: Arial, verdana, tahoma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;"><span style="color: #888888; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/EEW%20award.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="240" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p class="bodytext" style="margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; color: #6c6c6c; font-family: Arial, verdana, tahoma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/EEW%20gallery%201.jpg" alt="" width="468" height="360" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our Products/Services Coverage</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Offshore</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Pipelines</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Oil &amp; Gass Treatment Plants</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Power Plant Contruction</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Chemical &amp; Petrochemical plants</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Construction for Civil, Harbor, Pressure Vessal, Machinery</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">CRA Pipes</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Customised Fabrication Program</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Value Added Secondary Process</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/EEW%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="188" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #000000;"><em><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">"It''s really great to work for a company which is having</span><span>&nbsp;</s