quot;; color: #333333;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal;">Photo Copyright:natsteel.com.sg</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #333333;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal;"><br /></span></span></p>', 'http://www.natsteel.com.sg/', 1, 0, 36, 2665, '2013-07-17 16:50:31', '2013-10-23 11:53:49'),
(39, 1075, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Oriwise%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=37,+Jalan+Sutera+Tanjung+8%2F2,+Taman+Sutera+Utama,+81300+Skudai&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.501052,103.694918&amp;sspn=0.052253,0.077162&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=37+Jalan+Sutera+Tanjung+8%2F2,+Taman+Sutera+Utama,+81300+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We were awarded a prestigious award as runner up in the <strong>Interior Design and Construction competition</strong> organized by C.I.D.B in 2005.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We have also been awarded the <strong>Best Colour Award</strong>, <strong>2 Silver Award</strong>s (Residential Show House Category) and <strong>Winner</strong> (Kitchen Category) as runner up in the <strong>InteriCAD ID Award 2010</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Beside that, some of our completed works have received commendations from the Malaysian Institute of Architects (Southern Chapter).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Another milestone is in achieving the <strong>ISO 9001:2008 certification</strong> awarded by DAS Certification Ltd.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are registered with C.I.D.B as a grade G4 contractor and a member of <strong>Johor Interior Designer Association</strong> (JIDA).</span></p>\r\n<div><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Oriwise%20value.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></div>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Oriwise%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="399" height="592" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">At Oriwise Sdn Bhd, our employees are our most valuable assets. We help our people realize their potentials and expand their capacities. We personalize their career path and structure their training and development activities. We encourage them to think differently, to be innovative and to strive for excellence.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/oriwise%20testimonial2.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="500" /></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Oriwise%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="280" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">These outstanding individuals are steering us towards our goal and our reputation for reliability, innovation and cost effectiveness.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo source:oriwise.com.my</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_4408366_young-caucasian-engineer-with-blueprints-in-the-office.html">fotum / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.oriwise.com.my/welcome/', 1, 0, 12, 1519, '2013-07-30 10:44:02', '2014-03-04 12:16:02'),
(40, 2965, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/muda%20packaging%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Muda+pacific+jalan+persiaran+teknologi&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.540647,103.667679&amp;sspn=0.392618,0.617294&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Muda+pacific+jalan+persiaran+teknologi&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;cid=351910104417377939&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">Muda Packaging Indsutries thus enjoy being the key local player in the manufacturer of special die-cut cartons. Inview of Malaysia''s current export oriented industrialization process and the global emphasis on increased use of environment-friendly products, the timely arrival of Muda''s new product range is expected to boost the local packaging industry and enhance Malaysia''s export industry.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/MC%20pack%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="249" height="567" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">"Here, you can learn from people with different knowledge and experience.Development and self-improvement give me a lot of satisfaction"</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/MC%20pack%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_15043250_group-of-office-workers-looking-at-digital-tablet-and-smiling.html">dragonimages / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.muda.com/products_pkg.php', 1, 0, 7, 2121, '2013-08-12 12:00:05', '2014-08-22 13:50:11'),
(41, 2660, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Xin%20Hwa%20Transport%20Cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No.+2,+Jalan+Permatang+2,+Kempas+Baru,++81200+Johor+Bahru,+Johor,+Malaysia&amp;aq=&amp;sll=2.100664,103.504944&amp;sspn=1.56994,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Permatang+2,+Kempas+Permatang,+81200+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Xin%20Hwa%20Transport%20Logo.jpg" alt="" width="151" height="98" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Reliable Services</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">To ensure measures are meticulously taken to continuously improve and maintain high quality services in the provision of efficiency, timely delivery, reliability and cost-effectiveness for Total Clients'' Satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Committed Team</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">To ensure a conducive and rewarding work environment that promotes high level commitment and dedication, strong teamwork, harmonious relationship and winning spirit amongst employees in order to strive for excellence, professionalism and market leadership.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Innovative Systems &amp; Technology</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">To constantly upgrade and enhance state-of-art logistic system and technology for greater efficiency and personalized services to achieve unrivalled competitiveness and innovation.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Xin%20Hwa%20Transport%20Gallery.jpg" alt="" width="322" height="535" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Directly after college I was looking for an organization that understood the importance of supporting and investing in their people. Xin Hwa Trading &amp; Transport had help me set and achieve my career goals.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Xin%20Hwa%20Transport%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>', 'http://www.freightforwarder.com.my/index.html', 1, 1, 5, 2702, '2013-08-12 12:35:00', '2015-08-04 11:33:22'),
(42, 769, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20Cover%20Page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kimlun+Sdn.+Bhd.+city+square&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.461624,103.764088&amp;sspn=0.01227,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Kimlun+Sdn.+Bhd.+city+square&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;cid=17970691285875661261&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20Berhad%20Vision.jpg" alt="" width="482" height="267" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20Values%20and%20vision.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="130" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Photo copyright: kimlun.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Since 2002, we have completed over 200 projects of varying sizes, scope and contract value. To illustrate the diversity of the projects we have undertaken / are undertaking as well as our customer base, we set out below some of our building and infrastructure construction projects:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="250" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20gallery2.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="240" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Kimlun%20gallery3.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-size: 10px;">Photo copyright: kimlun.com</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-size: 10px;"><br /></span></span></p>', '<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/kimlun%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="267" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are a construction company with PKK Class A license and ISO 9001:2000 certification. Our core business involved in building construction and civil engineering projects in Johor Bahru area. In line with our rapid expansion, we are inviting suitable and qualified candidates for our opening positions</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="//www.youtube.com/v/HhNLm0shlaY?hl=en_US&amp;version=3" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/v/HhNLm0shlaY?hl=en_US&amp;version=3" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: kimlun.com</p>', 'http://www.kimlun.com/kimlun-corp/index.php', 1, 0, 7, 1560, '2013-08-20 13:02:11', '2013-11-26 10:10:18'),
(43, 841, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No.+408,+Jln+Pekeliling,+Kaw+Perindustrian+Pasir+Gudang,+81700+Pasir+Gudang&amp;sll=1.461645,103.764088&amp;sspn=0.013063,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Pekeliling,+81700+Pasir+Gudang,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Synthomer develops and markets polymers used in a wide range of industries to create and enhance everyday consumer products.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Within the commercial organisation, marketing and technical services are organised into six global Strategic Business Units (SBUs), working closely with regional sales organisations in Europe, Asia, Middle East, South Africa and North America. The Business Units are supported by technology groups specialised in different product chemistries and co-located with marketing and technical services to ensure fast innovation, strong customer focus and rapid speed to market of new products.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20CR%20value.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="130" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Synthomer is committed to managing its business in a safe and responsible manner. For us responsibility means economic, environmental and social responsibility, so we work with customers, suppliers, employees, shareholders and the communities around our sites to improve our environmental performance, health, safety and security. &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;"><br /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Corporate Resonsibility</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Sustainbility</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">SHE</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">CLP</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Quality</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Certifications</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #3366ff;"><span style="color: #564b47; font-family: Verdana, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Our People</span></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px;">Photo copyright: synthomer.com</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Synthomer is active in all major industrial regions of the globe: Europe, North America, South America, the Middle East, Africa and Asia. We also have a network of carefully selected and trained distributors and agents.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="260" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We provide spezialised product portfolios and customer support through our six strategic business units (SBU). They are your partner for developing innovative products, materials and solutions for:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20gallery%202.jpg" alt="" width="256" height="233" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 16px;">Markets &amp; Products</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Paper &amp; Board</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Construction &amp; Coatings</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Health &amp; protection</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Carpet, compounds &amp; foam</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Functional Polymer</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Performance Polymer</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Photo copyright: synthomer.com</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<p><span style="color: #4c4a4a; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px;"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n</ul>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our employees are valued for their dedication and passion.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The performance culture of our company incorporates a sustainable Human Resources development programme that supports diversity and equal opportunities across the globe. Our Health and Safety programme also supports our employees to realise their full potential. Investing in our people enables us to be a more attractive employer with competitive salary/benefit packages.</span></p>\r\n<div><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="260" /></div>', 'http://www.synthomer.com/', 1, 0, 9, 3137, '2013-08-20 13:53:13', '2014-04-05 10:37:36'),
(44, 1153, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hiewa%20Auto%20Gallery%20Cover%20Page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Toyota+%40+Jalan+Persiaran+Desa+Tebrau+Taman+Desa+Tebrau+81100+Johor+Bahru+Johor&amp;aq=1&amp;oq=Jalan+Persiaran+Desa+Tebrau,+Taman+Desa+Tebrau,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;sll=1.551436,103.792537&amp;sspn=0.006531,0.009645&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Toyota+%40&amp;hnear=Jalan+Persiaran+Desa+Tebrau,+Taman+Desa+Tebrau,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=4599818716847363228&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Moving Forward</span></strong></em></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">"Continuous improvement". Otherwise known as kaizen, this is a philosophy that is deeply entrenched in the culture at Toyota.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company''s global success and leadership prominence in the international automotive market today stem from this belief which emphasises the removal of non-value adding operations or waste, across its 4 principal areas of production &ndash; Planning and Design, Implementation, Evaluation and Assessment/Reassessment.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Diligently practised since our earliest days, the rewards of kaizen have resulted in, time and again, substantial cost reduction, waste minimalism and increased efficiency. All of which are shared benefits enjoyed by both our valued customers and the organisation.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Kaizen is employed at every facet on all levels within Toyota, enabling us to collectively embrace every challenge as an opportunity to only become better, stronger and always at the forefront &ndash; not only as a corporation, but more importantly, for our customers.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HieWa%20Auto%20Gallery%20Service%20Centre.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="569" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We strive to deliver what our customers value most: the quality, durability and reliability of a Toyota vehicle.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hiewa%20Auto%20Gallery%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /><br /></span></p>', 'www.toyota.com.my', 1, 0, 36, 1902, '2013-08-22 16:43:09', '2013-12-03 12:24:19'),
(45, 1189, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/MTU%20services%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=MTU+Services+(Malaysia)+Sdn+Bhd&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.671539,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=MTU+Services+(Malaysia)+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=&amp;radius=15000&amp;t=m&amp;cid=434084180388222546&amp;z=13&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/MTU%20services%20values.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="530" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11px;">photo copyright:Msm.net.my</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Services</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Full Maintenance, Repair and Overhaul services</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Specialised services with special tools &amp; sophisticated equipment</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Project Management in the maintenance of assets</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Management of assets</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Management Support for operations</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Advisory services to clients</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Logistics planning</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Configuration Management &amp; Condition Monitoring Services</span><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Remanufacturing</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/MTU%20services%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="569" height="434" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;">photo copyright:Msm.net.my</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&l