(51, 873, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%20%26%20T%20Holiday%20tour.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=19,+Jalan+Kuning+Dua+Taman+Pelangi,+80400+Johor+Bahru,+Johor,++West+Malaysia.&amp;aq=&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.671539,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=19+Jalan+Kuning+2,+Taman+Pelangi,+80400+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To provide good services to our customer and ensure they will have a great holiday, transportation is the first impression they received, therefore we are very particular and be sure our key word PUNCTUALITY is always carries out. Our present strengths of coaches which carries the Bas Persiaran License.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%20%26%20T%20Tour%20Value.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In midst of this fascinating, country with its friendly people, B&amp;T Holiday Tours Sdn Bhd have developed a series of exciting and highly popular overland discovery tours that enable the discovery of all aspects of this fascinating land of many cultures.</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&lsquo; One Stop Center&rdquo; providing full travel agent and tour operator services as follows :-</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Airlines Reservation &amp; Ticketing ( International &amp; Domestic )</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Worldwide Travel Packages</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Malaysia Tours</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Company Incentive Tours</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Local &amp; Worldwide Hotel Reservation</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Travel Insurance</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Application of Visa</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Hire of Coach and Combi</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Cruises &amp; etc&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<div><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%20%26%20T%20Tour%20Gallery.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="400" /></div>\r\n<div>photo copyright: bnt.com.my</div>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The instructors were exceptional and really knowledgeable. &nbsp;I made lots of new friends and had a great time.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I want to take this opportunity to say a heartfelt ''Thank You'' to you for your travel expertise over the years</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%20%26%20T%20Tour%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="200" /></p>', 'http://www.bnt.com.my/', 1, 0, 22, 1142, '2013-09-12 10:46:19', '2013-12-23 15:55:40'),
