(54, 1280, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Genetec%20Technology%20Berhad%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=GENETEC+TECHNOLOGY+BERHAD+(445537-W)+Bandar+Baru+Bangi+Selangor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=genetec+&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.671539,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=GENETEC+TECHNOLOGY+BERHAD+(445537-W)&amp;hnear=Bandar+Baru+Bangi,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=11076193377696487724&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Vision</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To Be the Most Competitive and World Leader in Industrial Automation.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong>Genetec Value</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Innovative, Competitive, Pragmatism, Right Attitude, Persistence.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Respect for Individual, Integrity, Courageous, Teamwork, Technology Excellence.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Genetec was incorporated in 1997 and began operation in 1998 providing assembly automation and engineering services to various industries and have grown ever since.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Genetec has technical expertise to support a diversify industry across the board,</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 11pt;">such as:</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span><em>Automotive</em></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-left: 30px;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Consumer product</span></em></div>\r\n<div style="padding-left: 30px;"><em><span st