(55, 1436, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Local%20Basic%20Cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Local+Basic+Sdn.+Bhd.+Taman+Nusajaya+Industri+1+Gelang+Patah+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=local+basic&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=13.316178,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Local+Basic+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=Taman+Nusajaya+Industri+1,+Gelang+Patah,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Introducing the One-Stop Solution</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">At Local Basic, our service does not stop at providing the ability to meet all your requirements, but from casting to the final assembly process, we are in total control of the quality of the product and its delivery.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our consistent ability to meet deadlines with products only of the best quality, has no doubt, garnered us a place among other leading names in the metal part casting industry.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We have earned ourselves a reputation of delivering only the best and this has gained us the trust and confidence of our customers.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We have pride in knowing that besides being cost effective and time efficient, we offer our customers a one-stop, quality service which is second to none.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We are dedicated in being a specialist in all areas of metal manufacturing processes.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Local%20Basic%20Vision.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="160" /><br /></span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our production facility is divided into four categories:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">â– <span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Die-Casting</span></p>\r\n<p><sp