(58, 1587, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Anka%20Tackle%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Anka+Tackle+Corporation+Sdn+Bhd+Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang+Ulu+Tiram+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=anka+t&amp;sll=1.556592,103.819773&amp;sspn=0.013964,0.01929&amp;g=No.+26,+Jalan+Masyhur+1,+Taman+Desa+Cemerlang,+81800+Ulu+Tiram,+Johor&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Anka+Tackle+Corporation+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang,+Ulu+Tiram,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=18235495007119525900&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are most self-critical of our own work process and development. Coupled with our stringent quality control system, we consistently produce high quality products that meet our customers&rsquo; satisfaction. Our rods are the choice of many professional anglers, with many rods playing a part in breaking IGFA records.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/anka%20tackle%20values.jpg" alt="" width="356" height="561" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">photo copyright:ankatackle.com</span></span></p>', '<p>\r\n<object width="420" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/t3y0r0fqcoc?hl=en_GB&amp;version=3" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/t3y0r0fqcoc?hl=en_GB&amp;version=3" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">One of the great advantages of working at Anka Tackle has been the opportunity to work in various departments and to be involved in many different projects. Being in control from raw materials to finish products enable us to implement our strict quality control system in the total production process, ensuring our products meet our customers&rsquo; required specification. Seeing our products grow and improve with each release has been our greatest satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Anka%20tackle%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="260" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_15360585_happy-fisherman-holding-a-grouper.html">sablin / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.ankatackle.com/', 1, 0, 42, 1316, '2013-10-06 14:54:40', '2014-06-15 12:31:29'),
(59, 1570, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/LG%20telco%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=LGtel+Co.+(M)+Sdn+Bhd+Taman+Sentosa+Johor+Bahru+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Lgtel+co&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=14.229989,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=LGtel+Co.+(M)+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Taman+Sentosa,+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=7332795137105929324&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As an authorised dealer for Digi Store, our vision is inline with Digi Telecommunication.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our vision is to be a company that is always ''Changing the Game''. We do this by constantly pushing boundaries, defining new standards, and ensuring continuous improvements in all parts of our business.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/LGtel%20co%20values.jpg" alt="" width="434" height="245" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/LGtel%20co%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="449" height="411" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:LGtel Co.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Working at a LGtel Co store everyday has something new to learn. I learned how to deal with various type of people with various types of problems and the number one goal was to solve the costumers problems. Basically make them happy was my number one goal. I have little complaint on management and coworkers. Everybody here play their role correctly.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/LGtel%20co%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="210" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:LGtel Co</p>', '', 1, 0, 38, 2170, '2013-10-06 15:32:17', '2014-02-14 13:30:54'),
(60, 1245, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/FCI%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Plo+205,+Jalan+Cyber+14,+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Senai+3&amp;aq=&amp;sll=5.419005,100.373529&amp;sspn=3.357252,4.938354&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Cyber+14,+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Senai+3,+81400+Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With a global footprint comprising of Asia, Europe and the Americas, FCI Electronics is well renowned and respected for our technological leadership, as well as innovative connector and cable assembly solutions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">At FCI Electronics, we design, and manufacture a wide array of hi-tech connector solutions for various market applications, including telecommunications, data storage, consumer electronics, as well as industrial and medical instrumentation.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Product offerings include Backplane, Power Solutions, Board/Wire to Board Connectors, Input/Output Connectors, Optical Interconnect, Cable Assemblies, Terminal Blocks and Flex Connectors.</span></p>\r\n<div><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/FCI%20values.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="330" /></div>\r\n<div>photo copyright:fci.com</div>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<object width="420" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/1Q8xJX5QqnY?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/1Q8xJX5QqnY?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/9uQI4FA1Yao?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/9uQI4FA1Yao?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Building a career in a global company from a younger age can broaden your potential and make your life dynamic and successful. FCI provides various opportunities for your career development. We look forward to receiving applicants from people filled with passion to contribute society through advanced technologies.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/FCI%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="230" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_15446824_portrait-of-a-lovely-business-lady-the-embodiment-of-enthusiasm-and-success-her-colleagues-working-i.html">dragonimages / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.fci.com/en.html', 1, 0, 26, 1352, '2013-10-06 16:18:54', '2014-03-05 14:15:43'),
(61, 1215, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/wheels%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Wheels+Electronics+Manufacturing+Sdn.+Bhd.+&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.462045,103.744565&amp;sspn=0.013964,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Wheels+Electronics+Manufacturing+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;cid=1074791037339772669&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">WHEELS has devoted years of experience and expertise in building our Manufacturing and R&amp;D strength to meet the expectations of both Malaysian and Overseas OEMs (Saudi Arabia, South Africa, Indonesia, Thailand, Hong Kong, Taiwan, Singapore, and Philippines).</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="float: left;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Wheels%20values.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="335" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11px;">photo copyright:wheels.net.my</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">WHEELS ELECTRONICS MANUFACTURING SDN. BHD. has become the leading manufacturer of a comprehensive range of quality automobile and home security systems, which include</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Receiver</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Immobilizer</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Alarm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Keyless Entry</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Power Window</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Central Locking</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Reverse Sensor/ sensor</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Curtain</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Siren</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Transmitter&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-Access Barrier System</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Wheels%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="463" height="309" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;">photo copyright:wheels.net.my</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Wheels Electronics Manufacturing has enlightened me on what an employer should be. From great benefits, approachable management, caring coworkers, opportunities to travel and a corporation that gives back. I am proud to say I work for Wheels and look forward to the new and innovative challenges I will face with them in the future.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/wheels%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="240" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_10527001_asian-business-colleagues-standing-in-a-row-and-smiling.html">sjenner13 / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.wheels.net.my/', 1, 0, 38, 1043, '2013-10-09 12:33:36', '2014-03-04 11:42:36'),
(62, 3989, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Desparkauto%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Despark+Auto+Sdn.+Bhd.+(Petaling+Jaya)+Usj+19+Subang+Jaya+Selangor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=despark&amp;sll=1.464069,103.744562&amp;sspn=0.013964,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Despark+Auto+Sdn.+Bhd.+(Petaling+Jaya)&amp;hnear=Usj+19,+Subang+Jaya,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=6037537304116432292&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;">Despark Auto Academy designed programs to train students with practical knowledge, with theory support in automotive technology and solid product knowledge according to the established international standards.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;"><img style="float: left;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Despark%20values.jpg" alt="" width="497" height="250" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;">photo copyright:desparkauto.edu.my</span></p>', '<p>\r\n<object width="560" height="315" data="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/CbGD3Jbcev4?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" />\r\n<param name="src" value="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/CbGD3Jbcev4?version=3&amp;hl=en_GB" />\r\n<param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Despark provides a great friendly atmosphere that brings together people from all work of life to combine and provide an effective , high level service for its clients.The training courses that are provided are really exciting and the opportunity to climb the ladder within Despark excites me</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Despark%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="405" height="220" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px;">photo copyright:desparkauto.edu.my</span></p>', 'http://www.desparkauto.edu.my/', 1, 1, 35, 2091, '2013-10-09 13:00:36', '2015-08-04 11:43:57'),
(63, 1601, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Serba%20wangi%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=SERBA+WANGI+JH+SDN.+BHD.+Jalan+Idaman+1%2F1+Taman+Perindustrian+Senai+Senai+Johor&amp;aq=2&amp;oq=serba+wangi&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=14.229989,19.753418&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=SERBA+WANGI+JH+SDN.+BHD.&amp;hnear=Jalan+Idaman+1%2F1,+Taman+Perindustrian+Senai,+81400+Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=5979604548523636136&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/serba%20wangi%20values.jpg" alt="" width="526" height="372" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Excellence in Product Quality</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We have set up rice mills to receive freshly harvested paddy at first hand from farmers. This enables us to implement quality control on the spot based on our quality standards of the rice being milled there before being sent to our branches for repacking.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Popular Products with Variety of Choices</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Consumers are assured of the availability of Organic Rice, Fragrant Rice, Brown Rice, Glutinous Rice, Basmati Rice, and Parboiled Rice from their nearby retail outlets. Our Company offers packaging of various sizes ranging from 1kg, 2kg, 5kg and up to 50kg.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Mission and Vision</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-To deliver products and services with the highest level of quality for maximum customers&rsquo; satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-To strengthen our current market position with the support of advertisements, promotions and greater publicity for building a stronger brand identity and enhancing the brand value and equity level.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">-To become a comprehensive and dominant force in the food distribution network whilst transforming into a well-diversified company.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/article/Serba%20Wangi%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="435" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:malaysiarice.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">A career at Serba Wangi will get you going with many growing opportunities.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As a multi award winner for one of the country&rsquo;s leading brands, Serba Wangi has served the rice business for more than 30 years. Our portfolio has grown to hold branches nation wide.</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/serba%20wangi%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="240" height="350" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_19291486_cheering-group-of-businesspeople-isolated-against-a-white-background.html">dragonimages / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.malaysiarice.com/', 1, 0, 27, 1785, '2013-10-15 15:02:12', '2014-06-15 12:00:37');
