(64, 1629, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/CEL%20logistic%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cel+Logistics+Taman+Perindustrian+Berjaya+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=cel+logis&amp;sll=1.626071,103.682166&amp;sspn=0.006982,0.009645&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Cel+Logistics&amp;hnear=Taman+Perindustrian+Berjaya,+Skudai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=4213673563654975820&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Having a strong distribution and warehousing strategy is critical to your success in today&rsquo;s global environment. Cel Logistics Sdn Bhd understand your business and logistic needs.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px;">So whether it&rsquo;s a competitive rate for an urgent shipment or a strategic partner who can identify and create short-term efficiencies and build up long-term competitiveness, our team of logistics professionals is ready to help.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are glad to provide your company a total solution for the services below:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">1) <span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Land Freight &amp; Custom Brokerage</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">2)<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Warehousing , Picking &amp; Kitting</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">3)<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Machine Packing and re-location&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">4)<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Container Haulage</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">5)<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Value Added Service</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Cel%20logistics%20values.jpg" alt="" width="482" height="341" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/CEL%20logistic%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="565" height="355" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">"My co-workers are wonderful and I have met several friends through work. I also have the opportunity to work in several different areas. At Cel Logistics, people really care about your well being and want you to excel. You are not just a number in Cel Logistics."</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/cel%20logistics%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_19000754_manager-owner-or-businesspeople-in-a-warehouse-of-a-forwarding-agency-or-a-factory.html">kzenon / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 8, 3067, '2013-10-15 15:58:18', '2014-10-18 10:11:41'),
(65, 748, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/gosford%20leather%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Gosford+Leather+Industries+Sdn.+Bhd.+Jalan+Masai+Lama+Masai+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=gos&amp;sll=1.486785,103.882942&amp;sspn=0.006585,0.009645&amp;g=No.16,Jalan+Masai+Lama,+Bandar+Seri+Alam,+81750+Masai+Johor&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Gosford+Leather+Industries+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=Jalan+Masai+Lama,+Masai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=17730470509823301073&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We had achieved much success as proven by the appointment to be the authorized PDI supplier by renowned car importers. Our products are also exported overseas, with our key export markets namely Australasia, Japan, USA &amp; Middle East &amp; Singapore occupying 70% of our total capacity. Recognizing increasing overseas competition following trade liberalization, our company is actively seeking strategic partnerships. We had also reached cooperative understanding with other manufacturers in the industry for common capacity sharing.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gosford%20leather%20values.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="191" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gosford%20leather%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="547" height="446" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:gosfortseat.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In Gosford you will gain the ongoing and tremendous opportunities to continue to grow as a professional and as a person, to learn new experiences, to build lasting and productive partnerships, and all within a rewarding and engaging environment. Join us now !</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gosford%20leather%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="229" height="172" /></p>', 'http://www.gosfordseat.com/index.asp', 1, 0, 23, 1023, '2013-10-26 17:27:56', '2014-04-24 23:46:21'),
(66, 1723, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/ST%20switchgear%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=S-Team+Switchgear+(M)+Sdn.+Bhd.+Gelang+Patah+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=S+team&amp;sll=1.443069,103.60558&amp;sspn=0.006585,0.009645&amp;g=16,+Jalan+Mega+1%2F8,+Taman+Perindustrian+Nusa+Cemerlang,+79200+Nusajaya,+Johor&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Vision, Mission &amp; Values</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">By employing the best talent and technology, we are able to offer our customers cost-effective and reliable electrical engineering products and solutions for commercial, residential, industrial, data centre, pharmaceutical, marine and oil &amp; gas in Singapore as well as the Asian Region.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Meeting customers requirement is what we do best and continue to strive to do better each day. The importance of long lasting relationship built on trust and mutual interest are the vital driving force for Gathergates. Driven by passion for our work, we are committed to power up the world for all our clients and be a leading electrical solutions provider in Asia.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">One of our keys to success lies in co-operation where strength is sustained through unity. Through our unified efforts to achieve value and deliver benefits to our partners and clients, we are able to fulfil our mission and work towards emerging as the first choice for electrical solutions provider in Asia.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong>Vision</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">A Leading Electrical Solutions Provider in Asia.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Mission</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To identify and forge strong partnership, recruit and develop talent, adopt the best technologies to offer the best electrical solutions to all our customers, and achieve superior returns to our stakeholders.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Values</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Passion - the very element that gives life and meaning to Gathergates - the foundation of our unceasing quest for high Quality products and Service Excellence which can only be achieved through unsurpassed Teamwork</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/S%20Team%20switchgear%20values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="129" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/S%20team%20switchgear%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="605" height="421" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">"There are many reasons why we are proud to work at S Team Switchgear. We have learned and grown personally and professionally by working for a company whose employees have a diverse background of cultures and knowledge."</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/S%20Team%20switchgear%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="634" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:gathergates.com</p>', 'http://www.gathergates.com/index.shtml', 1, 0, 35, 1584, '2013-11-01 13:08:43', '2014-08-11 12:34:16'),
(67, 1781, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/ETECH%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=ETECH+SYSTEM+AUTOMATION+SDN+BHD+Jalan+Dedap+18+Taman+Johor+Jaya+Johor+Bahru+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Etech+sys&amp;sll=1.499581,103.846153&amp;sspn=0.006585,0.009645&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;output=embed', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The Company prides itself of being able to provide excellent after sales service support for all its products and systems. In fact maintenance services and repairs are in themselves a major activity of the Company. Our unique and proven systems reap immediate savings and improvements to the efficiency of customers operations.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our objective has always been to create a network of satisfied Customers, and for that to happen, we have to ensure we offer only the best products and the best customer service always.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/ETECH%20values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="220" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our core business is providing highly specialized value-added office and surveillance solutions</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Products such as CCTV Surveillance Systems &amp; Security Equipment, Door Access, PABX Keyphone System, Office Automation, Multimedia &amp; IT Solutions and many others complement the services we offer to our customers. We specialised in the field of designing, supplying, installing and commissioning, and all works done by our own technical staff</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/ETECH%20product%20%26%20services.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="340" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As ETECH is constantly growing and the Customer Care Department handles more and more high profile projects the project team was created. I was happy to grow within the organization and be a part of this new team.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/ETECH%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="280" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_10089280_young-business-woman.html">leungchopan / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.etech2u.com/', 1, 0, 22, 681, '2013-11-14 15:46:20', '2014-02-18 15:48:50'),
(68, 239, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lipidchem%20banner.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Lipidchem+Sdn.+Bhd.+Bandar+Seri+Alam+Masai+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=lidipcchem&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.784065,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We offer thirty five years of experience in product development, production and quality control and customer service in our specialised fields and are proud of the trust that we have gained from our customers world-wide.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Innovation in technology and product development and total customer satisfaction are the cornerstones of our corporate culture. The relationship begins with us making every effort to understand our customers'' requirements thoroughly. Built upon that will be a fully engaged working relationship and when necessary will involve the development of new products to meet their exact needs.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/lipidchem%20values.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="240" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_18736409_male-scientist-using-tablet-computer-in-laboratory.html">stockbroker / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We manufacture various beads for fatty acids, animal feed supplements, food emulsifiers</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lipidchem%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="535" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><em><span style="color: #888888;">We are expanding our business and looking for interested candidates</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">"I set my sights on working for Lipidchem based on its reputation and its focus on providing opportunities for career progression in the chemical industry. I could progress within the company because of their support and encouragement of personal and professional development for all employees"</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lipidchem%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_11048122_portrait-of-beautiful-young-businesswoman.html">leaf / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.lipidchem.com/default.aspx', 1, 0, 27, 663, '2013-11-21 12:23:40', '2014-03-04 11:47:15'),
(69, 1867, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/JBB%20builders%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=20-01,+Jalan+Sri+Perkasa+2%2F18,+Taman+Tampoi+Utaman,+81200+JB&amp;aq=&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=16.163565,26.784668&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=20+Jalan+Sri+Perkasa+2%2F18,+Taman+Tampoi+Utama,+81200+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #444444;">Over the year with continuous hard work, perseverance, beliefs in management efficiency and the combination of young, energetic and experienced human resources portfolio, we have successfully propelled into varies natures of construction work such as river dredging works (Marine Engineering), earthworks, road and drainage works (Infrastructure Works), construction of palm oil mill (Oil &amp; Gas Industry) and construction of food processing plant with HACCP standard (Food Industry).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #444444;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #444444;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/JBB%20Builders%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="220" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #444444;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_16969776_colleagues-discussing-the-blueprint-in-office.html">dragonimages / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;">A highly acclaimed organization with the drive to achieve greater heights, JBB Builder (M) Sdn Bhd is moving forward with a Vision to be a prominent player in the field of Engineering and Construction. It is the objective of JBB to constantly provide excellent quality products and valuable services to our clients, and at the same time, create a better quality of life for our employee and our stakeholders.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/JBB%20Builders%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="245" height="669" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #444444; mso-ansi-language: EN-MY; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">JBB Builders management has a great ability to tap the potential in its employees and put them in a place where they can succeed.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company continuously monitors the performance and ensures that any achievement doesn''t go unnoticed but is suitably rewarded.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/JBB%20Builders%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="230" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_13920514_operator-of-a-excavator.html">ndoeljindoel / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 16, 5601, '2013-12-01 11:59:57', '2014-03-17 12:05:51'),
(70, 1880, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Siacon%20Technology%20Banner.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+Jalan+Canggih+2+Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang+Ulu+Tiram+Johor&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.549216,103.821391&amp;sspn=0.00754,0.013078&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Canggih,+Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang,+81800+Ulu+Tiram,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Siacon Technology Sdn Bhd is a leader in providing value-added construction services to our customers by creating a successful partnership with them throughout the construction process. We ensure the success of our company through repeat and referral business achieved by customer satisfaction in all areas including timeliness, attention to detail and service-minded attitudes.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Siacon%20Technology%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="115" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We have completed over 100 projects in our timeline. Below are some samples of our quality jobs</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Siacon%20Technology%20Gallery.jpg" alt="" width="306" height="668" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">I treated Siacon Technology as a second family. The people are supportive and the work is challenging. Our company culture is based on open communication, dedication and teamwork. I feel that I have access to upper management, and more importantly, they listen. New ideas are encouraged and our forward-thinking leadership is always looking for ways to improve the way we perform for our customers.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Siacon%20Technology%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="406" height="270" /></p>', '', 1, 0, 3, 3251, '2013-12-01 13:04:28', '2015-05-09 15:21:36'),
(71, 1827, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Promelight%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=jalan+Silc3+kawasan+silc+79200+nusajaya&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.557807,103.64502&amp;sspn=0.253965,0.41851&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=jalan+Silc+3+kawasan+silc+79200+nusajaya&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;z=11&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our goal is to deliver affordable, clean and renewable energy to global customers striving to achieve economic sustainability and better environment. The sense of environmental responsibility continuously drives our dedication and passion for new energy.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/promelight%20values.jpg" alt="" width="314" height="214" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:promelight.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Promelight%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="669" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:promelight.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">My background was an electrical technician for power grid. I started to discover that i could help to change the world after my friend introduce me to Promelight Technology.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Beside my job satisfaction, im also contributing back to the healtier environment and my children. Come &amp; join our team now!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Promelight%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="220" /></p>', 'http://promelight.com.my/index.php', 1, 0, 33, 1702, '2013-12-01 14:11:02', '2014-03-05 14:14:59'),
(72, 1751, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lionmas%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No.+3,+Jalan+Masai+Lama,+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Kota+Putri+1,+Masai&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.499934,103.850864&amp;sspn=0.00754,0.013078&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=1+Jalan+Masai+Lama,+81750+Masai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Today LIONMAS has grown into a multi-chain store company by establishing 24 network branches spanning over Johor State with its HQ and factory warehouse measuring about 25,000 sq ft located in Masai, Johor, and another 3 network branches in Selangor Sate</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/lionmas%20logo.jpg" alt="" width="335" height="135" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">COMPANY MISSION</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">Our mission is to be an outstanding corporation in our core businesses by providing products and services of superior value to our customers and create a sustainable business through consistent long term growth in volume and profitability.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">SERVICE MISSION</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">Delight customer at all times with the mindset of "customer is always right".</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">BRANDING MISSION</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">Create, enhance and protect company&rsquo;s positive image and establish customers&rsquo; trust in LIONMAS trademark.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">PEOPLE MISSION</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">Develop and maximize our people potential to deliver outstanding results.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">BUSINESS PARTNER MISSION</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;">Build a rewarding and long-lasting partnership by adopting win-win option in our business relation with partners.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.545454025268555px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Recognized as one of the most popular household name in Johor state for its Easy Payment Scheme and strongly supported by a well-established database of loyal customers, LIONMAS is committed to improve every aspects of its business to provide its customers better service in terms of more varied product choices, competitive price, short delivery time &amp; excellent after-sales services.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lionmas%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="565" height="400" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Consumer electronics is an exciting industry with fast product life cycles and an great opportunity to identify unmet needs and develop customer solution.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I enjoy working here everyday, working with my co-workers and to show them direction if they need it. I feel as though this company has taught me how to interact with others and what is the best way to approch someone in a nice manner.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Lionmas%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="380" height="430" /></p>', 'http://lionmas.com/', 1, 0, 4, 2377, '2013-12-01 15:30:16', '2014-08-06 14:37:03'),
(73, 1712, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gintell%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+12,+Jalan+Persiaran+KIP+1,+Taman+Perindustrian+KIP,+kepong&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.486499,103.883671&amp;sspn=0.00754,0.013078&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=12+Persiaran+Kip+1,+Taman+Perindustrian+Kip,+52200+Kuala+Lumpur,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Brand Values</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Continuous efforts in brand building, marketing strategies combined with extensive market research are key factors behind the success of the company.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company main priority is customer satisfaction through GINTELL&rsquo;s philosophy of integrity and honesty. The core values of the company include responsibility, respect and teamwork</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gintell%20values.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="400" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: gintell.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our products are developed and diversified mainly into 4 categories: These massage ranges from massage chairs , massage beds, foot and handheld massagers, slimming and beauty products and a range of exercising equipment.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gintell%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="672" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n<object width="420" height="315">\r\n<param name="movie" value="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/AVoSRZxyFak?version=3&amp;hl=en_US" />\r\n<param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" />\r\n<param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/v/AVoSRZxyFak?version=3&amp;hl=en_US" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always"></embed>\r\n</object>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: gintell.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Gintell is an exciting company to work for, it has establishment in various countries with lots of opportunities. At every stage we were mentored to refine our capabilities, provided with immense opportunities and was given a free hand for execution. This company believes in nurturing young talent and does not shed away from giving responsibility to youngsters. Equally important has been the support from management all along the way.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Gintell%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="240" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_18544607_business-team-joining-in-a-huddle-isolated-on-white-background.html">ximagination / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.gintell.com/v1/en/main.aspx', 1, 0, 35, 992, '2013-12-01 16:50:17', '2014-03-24 16:33:48'),
(74, 1888, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/M%20ficher%20tech%20cover%20page.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=M-Fischer+Tech+Sdn.+Bhd.+Jalan+Petaling+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Dato+Onn+Johor+Bahru+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=m+fischer+tech&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=2.031066,3.348083&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=M-Fischer+Tech+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=Jalan+Petaling,+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Dato+Onn,+80350+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=7843530177139190694&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our Vision</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Our vision is to strive to becoming a world class manafacturer by leveraging on our experience and continous development and acquisition of new technologies to meet our customers'' sophisticated product requirement.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/M%20ficher%20tech%20values1.jpg" alt="" width="477" height="454" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong>Business Ethics Policy</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">No Corruption, Extortion or Embezzlement</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">The highest standards of integrity are to be expected in all business interactions. Any and all forms of corruption, extortion and embezzlement are strictly prohibited resulted in immediate termination and legal action.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Disclosure of Information</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Information regarding business activities structure, financial situation and performance is to be disclosed in accordance with applicable regulations and prevailing industry practices.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">No Improper Advantage</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bribes or other means of obtaining undue or improper advantage are not to be offered or accepted.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Fair Business, Advertising and Competition</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Standards of fair business, advertising and competition are to be upheld. Means to safeguard customers'' information should be available.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Whistleblowers</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Programs that ensure the protection of supplier and worker whistleblower confidentiality are to be maintained.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Community Engagement</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Community engagement is encouraged to help foster social and economic development.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Protection of Intellectual Property</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Intellectual property rights are to be respected; transfer of technology and know-how is to be done in a manner that protects intellectual property rights.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/M%20ficher%20tech%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="600" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/M%20ficher%20tech%20gallery2.jpg" alt="" width="452" height="203" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:fischer.com.sg</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">The working environment at m fischer tech is energetic and positive, always cutting edge.I am driven to be passionate about my work as I work with a group of people who feel the same. The company values are the same as mine and that makes me feel at home.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/M%20fischer%20tech.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_10336538_corporate-themed-image-of-business-people.html">sjenner13 / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.fischer.com.sg/g_compan.html', 1, 0, 34, 922, '2013-12-05 16:39:19', '2014-03-04 12:07:37'),
(75, 1535, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hakko%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No+31+Jln+Mutiara+Emas+5%2F13,Tman+Mount+Austin,81100+Johor+&amp;aq=&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=16.163565,26.784668&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=31+Jalan+Mutiara+Emas+5%2F13,+Taman+Mount+Austin,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Hakko Corporation has won numerous awards for outstanding achievements in soldering technology since their establishment in 1952. This includes an award from the Administration of Science And Technology Agency, Japan, for developing the technology for temperature control systems in soldering equipment.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In Singapore, Hakko Products shows its commitment to technical education and training through its Memorandum of Understanding with ITE College West in December 2010. The signed memorandum allows an exchange of latest soldering technology and knowhow between Hakko Products and ITE.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hakko%20values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="125" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="line-height: 115%;">Our core products, Your needs satisfaction</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="line-height: 115%;"><br /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">As a globally recognized leader in soldering products, Hakko provides reliable solutions to meet your soldering needs. Our main business is trading Hakko brand soldering &amp; desoldering equipment, static control products and professional hand tools.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">We strive to exceed your expectations by delivering advanced soldering technologies for a wide range of products and working environments.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Hakko Products Pte Ltd also has a network for complementary, soldering-related products.This includes LPKF PCB prototyping equipment, HK Technologies laser-cut stencils and templates, Jtec magnifying lamps, and Vessel drill bits.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hakko%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="474" height="330" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">photo copyright: hakko.com.sg</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">The company''s senior leaders have truly internalized the goals and objectives they have laid out for their staff. <span>&nbsp;</span>People smiled; people were helpful; people were motivated; people were genuine.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hakko%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_8138332_cute-business-woman-give-you-a-cup-of-coffee-in-office.html">elwynn / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.hakko.com.sg/', 1, 0, 18, 950, '2013-12-22 12:05:46', '2015-04-19 13:35:25'),
(76, 1943, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Hwahin%20Cover%202.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=No+5+,+Jalan+Setia+3%2F2,+Taman+Setia+Indah+81100+Johor+Bahru.+Johor&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.571599,103.756814&amp;sspn=0.00754,0.013078&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=5+Jalan+Setia+3%2F2,+Taman+Setia+Indah,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Our principal business/ activities are those of a general contract in the construction line specializing in the following fields:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Earthworks, drainage &amp; roadworks</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Highway &amp; interchange construction</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Bridges &amp; retaining walls</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Commercial building</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%;">Factory</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company is also diversifying into Readymix concrete Industry as well as Precast Concrete products.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;">&nbsp;<img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HwaHin%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="210" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="line-height: 115%;">Our successfully completed projects<