ves</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/hwahin%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_22367534_portrait-young-asian-engineer-in-factory.html">norgal / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 32, 1213, '2013-12-23 15:54:11', '2014-03-17 12:06:22'),
(77, 945, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/JuBin%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kawasan+Perindustrian+Terbau+III,+81100+Johor&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.732829,103.566742&amp;sspn=0.905948,1.674042&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kawasan+Perindustrian+Tebrau,+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our mission is to serve our customers by enhancing the beauty and aesthetic value of not just their homes, but their lifestyle as well. Hence, we always strive to provide only the best &ndash; unparalleled quality products and aftersales service. Also, by providing a variety of quality products all housed under one roof, we aim to help our customer save time and money when they&rsquo;re shopping with us.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">When you think of Ceramic Tiles in Malaysia, you will think of JUBIN BMS as your preferred choice!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/JuBin%20BMS%20values.jpg" alt="" width="502" height="230" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:jubinbms.com.my</p>', '<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">COTTO Tiles</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">COTTO tiles became the world&rsquo;s no.1 producer for ceramic goods in 2011 while attaining a number of prestigious design awards from distinctive designers around the world such as Spain and Italy.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">COTTO Sanitary ware &amp; Fittings</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">COTTO&rsquo;s innovative range of sanitary ware &amp; fittings includes installation for kitchens, bathrooms, toilets and shower areas. The entire range of products is designed to be elegant and distinct to appeal to the sense while maintaining their practicality and durability.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As with all COTTO&rsquo;s products, these are designed to be eco-friendly and to provide the right solution while meeting the highest standards.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">FIMA Water Faucet &amp; Tap Fittings</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">FIMA (Fabbrica Italiana Miscelatori Accessori), was founded by Carlo Fratinni in 1960, has been producing high-quality taps and fittings guided by the accurate analysis of the reality and the constant application of technology. Utilising the latest computerized &amp; robotic manufacturing technology, FIMA&rsquo;s products are guaranteed to longer and carries a warranty of at least 7 years.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">BMS PORCELAIN (Our OEM brand)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Offering a full &amp; wide range of the highest quality in porcelain products. Our OEM brand offers products such as bathroom, kitchen, and tiles installations at affordable prices catering to both the residential and commercial segment.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">EURANO Kitchen &amp; Bathroom products</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Specialising in customised design solutions to all kinds of bathroom and kitchen with a high emphasis on high quality, practical design and ease of use. Besides that, we provide our customers a one stop, all-in-one installation convenience where everything is covered: once the purchase decision has been made, everything will be taken car</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Jubin%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="400" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:jubinbms.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">JuBin is an awesome company to work for and I have recommended potential employees many times. I truly feel that I work with my family and my friends every day. I feel so blessed to work for such a great company.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Jubin%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="230" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_21879200_welcoming-image-of-female-collegues.html">sjenner13 / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.jubinbms.com.my/company-profile/', 1, 0, 10, 903, '2013-12-23 16:32:12', '2014-04-05 10:37:12');
