action plans to adapt successfully to market demand. My job is important as our priority is customer satisfaction in terms of quality, costs and delivery.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Honda%20Jobs.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="150" /></p>', '', 1, 0, 2, 3053, '2013-12-27 12:41:31', '2014-08-19 16:32:19'),
(79, 1962, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/HQ%20tool%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Pontian+Jalan+Ulu+Choh+Kampung+Ulu+Choh+Pekan+Nanas+Johor&amp;aq=1&amp;oq=ulu+choh+pontian&amp;sll=1.478784,103.590517&amp;sspn=0.060319,0.104628&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Ulu+Choh,+Kampung+Ulu+Choh,+81500+Pekan+Nanas,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">H Q Tool Industries Sdn Bhd was founded by Mr Lee Siew Kai in year 1991 with specialize in plastic injection molding, secondary process and CNC machining (turning &amp; milling). &nbsp;We manufacture high quality of bike and fishing&rsquo;s precision components with attained ISO 9001:2008 certification in year 2008. &nbsp;To achieve operation efficiency and compete efficiently in this market, thus, we have adopted technology such as robot arm and XY loader into our operation system in order to attain cost-effective. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/H%20Q%20TOOL%20GREETING%20ADS_HALF%20PAGE.jpg" alt="" width="380" height="410" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With our strong core values of quality orientation and customers&rsquo; satisfaction, H Q Tool proudly becomes the key vendor to Shimano Components in Malaysia over 20 years. Our continuously development, H Q Tool is starting to upgrade our existing team players&rsquo; technical knowledge and management skill as well and in the same time to patronize new generation in this industry.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Company%20building%20facade_H%20Q%20Tool_H%20Q%20Tool%20Ind.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Our Products &amp; Achievement</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/product%203_H%20Q%20Tool%20Ind.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/product%204_H%20Q%20Tool%20Ind.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/SCAN0000.JPG" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Contribution to social development &amp; help benefit society</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HQ%20tools%20testimonial2.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="230" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Company Trip</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HQ%20Tools%20testimonial3.jpg" alt="" width="440" height="280" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The core values of passion, partnership and performance. My team is one of the best parts of working with HQ Tool Industries</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HQ%20tool%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_1052903