(80, 1832, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Cover%20page%20Demand%20Options.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Demand+Options+Sdn.+Bhd.+Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang+Ulu+Tiram+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=demand+option&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.913054,3.348083&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Demand+Options+Sdn.+Bhd.&amp;hnear=Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang,+Ulu+Tiram,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=515810960345313761&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our specialization in the sphere of laser cutting, metal stamping, engineering and design, tool and die, prototyping, spray painting and electronics assembly in humidity controlled environment, have met our customers&rsquo; crucial manufacturing applications with a high degree of satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Demand%20Option%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="629" height="115" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our export markets inclusive of countries below:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Japan</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">HongKong</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">China</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Philippines</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">USA</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Singapore</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">India&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Thailand</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">DOSB&rsquo;s earnest compliance towards ISO Standards and Commitments has enabled us to offer a wide spectrum of quality services that has gained us extensive industrial recognition. Harnessed by a strong management and operation team who has spent multiple years at top MNCs, We have great confidence in measuring up to the most stringent Quality expectations and demands from all our valued customers.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Demand%20Option%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="423" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Demand%20Option%20gallery2.jpg" alt="" width="516" height="425" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our team is like a big family and I really cherish being in this environment. I have to work hard, but I&rsquo;m motivated by our commitment to our values &amp; customers. I also know that my own contribution is valued and that the company is willing to support and invest in me &ndash; helping me put together an excellent training program which will help me make a difference and meet my longer term in my career ladder</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Demand%20Option%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="350" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_742631_confident-business-partners-over-a-white-background--one-from-latin-american-and-one-from-asia.html">andresr / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.dosb.com.my/index.php', 1, 0, 16, 3248, '2014-01-02 13:06:57', '2015-01-18 03:29:42'),
(81, 2011, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Dover%20construction%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=18-01,+Jalan+Sagu+36+Taman+Daya,+81100+Johor+Bahru+&amp;aq=&amp;sll=4.140634,109.618148&amp;sspn=16.163565,26.784668&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=18+Jalan+Sagu+36,+Taman+Daya,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Developing our builders expertise is a primary goal of our construction services. &nbsp;We place well educated, trained skilled builders on our projects who understand construction means and methods, sound management processes and procedures, and who embrace the highest standards for excellence in the industry.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Dover%20construction%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="216" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Strong client relationships are highly important to us, because we believe that success is achieved through active, dedicated connections with our clients. &nbsp;We spend the time, utilize the talent, and maximize every tool at our disposal to continually innovate and improve how we deliver your next landmark project.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Some of our projects</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Dover%20construction%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="636" height="634" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">our most valuable resources are our people, who carry forth our traditions, values, and long-standing reputation for performance. &nbsp;We take pride in investing the time and energy to recruit the best talent in our industry. &nbsp;W