(82, 1692, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/EDMI%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Senai+Industrial+Park,+81400+Senai,+Johor&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.553002,103.648453&amp;sspn=0.22651,0.41851&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Senai+Industrial+Park,+81400+Senai,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With over 20 years&rsquo; experience of manufacturing smart meters and millions of EDMI smart meters installed worldwide, EDMI&rsquo;s products are tried and tested, giving you the confidence of working hand in hand with a company with a proven track record. Our focus on quality flows from the design phase through to our post sales service, giving you the peace of mind that you can then pass onto your customers. At EDMI we are dedicated to providing solutions for our customers. We are proud of our customer relationships and our partnership approach ensures that we deliver to customer requirements and exceed expectations.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Vision</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Global Energy Solution Leader</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Mission</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Challenge for advanced technologies, create new values and be responsible for better society through our energy solutions</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/EDMI%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="304" height="324" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;">photo copyright:edmi-meters.com</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;