(87, 2265, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Pyramid%20phase%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=87,+Taman+Mount+Austin,+81100+Johor+Bahru,&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.550342,103.773884&amp;sspn=0.007947,0.013078&amp;vpsrc=0&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Taman+Mount+Austin,+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;ll=1.547695,103.781058&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Pyramid Phase are a company with a focus customer service, with over 20 years of construction experience and with a staff of professional skilled in construction management, we are dedicated to superior workmanship and adhere strictly to our schedule and service commitments, safety delivery a quality product on time at a good value &amp; the best service is our priority!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/pyramid%20phase%20values.jpg" alt="" width="439" height="356" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span><span style="line-height: 17.633333206176758px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444;">W</span></span><span style="line-height: 17.633333206176758px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444;">e have completed quality prestiges projects of varying sizes, scope and contract value in Johor &amp; Kuala Terengganu. We have displayed a high level of collaboration while delivering an added value innovative approach to project delivery.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Some of our projects;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img sty