(88, 2318, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/deluxe%20circle%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=de+luxe+groups&amp;aq=&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.344934,2.213745&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=de+luxe+groups&amp;hnear=&amp;t=m&amp;cid=2253496129074146250&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The De Luxe Groups recognises its responsibilities and obligations to the society and consumers. Not only do we want to serve the community by providing the best, the healthiest, the most hygienic and safest quality product, we must also necessitate an extreme cautiousness to conscientiously implement, strengthen quality management and supervision, to convince that our products are safe to consume and to meet consumer requirements and expectations!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/deluxe%20circle%20values.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">6Cs&rsquo; Values</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Conviction: Attitude</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Creativity: Product</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Consciousness: Customer</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Commitment: Service</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Cohesiveness: Team</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; Contentment: Staff</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo coyright; www.deluxegroups.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/deluxe%20circle%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="374" height="617" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright; www.deluxegroups.com</p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The training makes us well equipped and empowered to do my job with excellence.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The strong "promote-from-internal" at Deluxe Circle Group is very attractive because we knew we would have the opportunity to experience multiple job roles within various departments.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We really enjoy being a part of the daily collaboration between operations, sales and quality control that is required to run an effective and efficient operation.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/deluxe%20circle%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="348" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright; www.deluxegroups.com</p>', 'http://deluxegroups.com/', 1, 0, 10, 2599, '2014-02-27 12:41:59', '2015-03-08 13:43:06'),
(89, 550, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%26G%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=B+%26+G+Concept+Engineering+Sdn+Bhd+Usj+21+Subang+Jaya+Selangor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=B%26G&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.545289,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=B+%26+G+Concept+Engineering+Sdn+Bhd&amp;hnear=Usj+21,+Subang+Jaya,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;cid=6140585425287896048&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;">Equipped with thorough know-how, profound passion and a team of certified professionals, we are able to create a series of advanced masterworks, all richly entwined with natural elements and environment-friendly approaches. With every single aspect is taken into account, we can assure you that our high quality developments are made to last for generations.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%26G%20dPristine%20Night.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="300" /><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%26G%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="420" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The career growth opportunities are endless due to B&amp;G forward thinking, open minded senior management. B&amp;G and the people here have given me the tools to learn and grow, both professionally and in my personal life</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/B%26G%20Testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="500" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '', 1, 0, 12, 5237, '2014-03-04 11:41:08', '2015-03-08 14:37:59'),
(90, 931, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Ajiya%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=PPU3+Taman+Perindustrian+Puchong+Utama,+47100+Puchong&amp;aq=&amp;sll=3.001324,101.608667&amp;sspn=0.011271,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+PPU+3,+Taman+Perindustrian+Puchong+Utama,+47100+Puchong,+Selangor&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">ARI is an established manufacturer of metal roll-forming products - metal roofing system, metal frame products, structural products, light-weight channel products, AriteQ&trade; metal ceiling and sun shade products in Malaysia. These products, under the brand name of AJIYA&reg;, are widely used in Malaysia and South East Asia countries.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Mission: To be " To Be The Most Preferred And Trusted Brand In S.E.A. "</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Ajiya%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="526" height="515" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright; http://www.ajiya.com/index.htm&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our product range from Roofing Industry, Metal Frame structure, Architectural, Light weight channel, Tempered Glass, Security Glass, Decorative Glass...</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Ajiya%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="203" height="596" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Photo copyright; &nbsp;http://www.ajiya.com/index.htm</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Ajiya taught me how to think in a creative way, sell, prototype, deliver emails, present at major conferences and much more. I really enjoy working for Ajiya because I''m able to participate in many interesting and exciting projects while having fun and doing what I''m good at.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;<img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Ajiya%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="240" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_11846487_portrait-of-a-beautiful-business-woman-working-on-her-desk-in-an-office-environment.html">ferli / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.ajiya.com/', 1, 0, 28, 1475, '2014-03-05 12:18:37', '2014-11-23 13:14:56'),
(91, 2599, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/PHHP%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jalan+Rawa+2+Taman+Desa+Cemerlang,+81100+Ulu+Tiram,+Johor&amp;aq=&amp;sll=1.560638,103.809986&amp;sspn=0.011283,0.01929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jalan+Rawa+2,+Taman+Desa+Jaya,+81100+Johor+Bahru,+Johor&amp;ll=1.560638,103.809986&amp;spn=0.011283,0.01929&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With a total of 16 branches and 6 stockists, PHHP is one of the direct selling companies with the most branches in Malaysia. It has also ventured into international markets- Singapore, Indonesia and Thailand. Furthermore, PHHP has set up a GMP-compliant health food products manufacturing factory to produce high quality products to benefit the customers.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">4 Core Missions</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">PHHP stand out from the rest by its unique philosophy of having four core missions:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Spread Health</span></em></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">PHHP promote its product through love and affection; thereby strictly adhere to high quality standard.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Spread Wealth</span></em></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our main asset is People, not only bringing success but also ensure quality life for everyone.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Spread Wisdom</span></em></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We believe in Life-long learning, letting every member of PHHP family gain from our education system. Through such training programme, they improve in all aspects including mental strength, sales technique and etc.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Spread Love</span></em></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">By living the spirit ''People Happily Helping People'', we send a message of mutual love and concern among each other. Let our people be the sunshine, hope and warmth of family and society. Our charity fund further promotes benevolence among all. We encourage our members to commit themselves to spread the power of love to every corner of the world.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/PHHP%20Gallery.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="500" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.phhp.com.my/en/</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">PHHP also provides different trainings, leadership programs and workshops in order to help staff &amp; partners to have better command to their success. With this great opportunity to have a better life, it is definitely a great chance worth to pursue!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/PHHP%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="298" height="191" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.phhp.com.my/en/</p>', 'http://www.phhp.com.my/en/', 1, 1, 33, 1007, '2014-03-14 12:09:14', '2015-08-04 11:46:04'),
(92, 534, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Pet%20Far%20Eastern%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Pet+Far+Eastern+(M)+Sdn+Bhd+Jalan+Persiaran+Selasih+Senai+Johor&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=pet+far&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.545289,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=&amp;ll=1.627324,103.651899&amp;spn=0.006295,0.006295&amp;t=m&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">VISION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Become a world class GREEN products provider</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">MISSION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Provide safe, reliable and environmental friendly products.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Enhance employee''s work-life harmony.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Advocate Corporate''s core values - Sincerity, Diligence, Thrift, Prudence and Innovation</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Pet%20Far%20Eastern%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="370" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Through training and excellent support from my managers and our training department, I have worked my way through the various positions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I thoroughly enjoy working and I work with a great team of staff, although at times it is very challenging and I can say that I get great job satisfaction from working in Pet Far Eastern.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Pet%20Far%20eastern%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="300" /></p>', 'http://www.petfar.com/usr/page.aspx?pgid=9', 1, 0, 32, 1136, '2014-04-01 15:33:00', '2014-08-11 11:53:03'),
(93, 1905, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Vanhoden%20cover.jpg', 'https://maps.google.com.my/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=vanhoden&amp;sll=2.047907,103.505343&amp;sspn=1.545289,2.469177&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=&amp;ll=1.532157,103.794301&amp;spn=0.006295,0.006295&amp;t=m&amp;output=embed', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">VANHODEN offers a wide range of stylish designed branded and luxury home furnishing products at best quality with fair prices. Our mission is to serve you the best and meet all customers satisfaction</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Vanhoden%20Values.jpg" alt="" width="376" height="282" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Vanhoden%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="396" height="602" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company takes care of its employees and treats them like family. The team I work with is very helpful. Everyone is willing to help and great to work with. As a team we&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px;">enjoy working with customer issues to make sure that all things get fixed so that customers are happy.</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/7796962_s.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Image credit: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/profile_carlosphotos">carlosphotos / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', '', 1, 1, 19, 1451, '2014-04-18 10:07:37', '2015-06-03 14:45:45');
