(96, 2547, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/sinkwang%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3987.6987057770853!2d102.97615!3d1.8677070000000027!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31d050b1ba7bb041%3A0x60a03557934f669d!2sSkin+Kwang+Platic+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1400986499571" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">SKPRB Group is principally involved in the manufacturing of plastic parts and components, precision mould making, the sub-assembly of electronic and electrical equipment and other secondary processes</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sinkwang%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="348" height="305" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As plastics have become an essential and integral part of all light to heavy engineering manufacturing components; fully aware of the intense demand on quality standards, SKP is fully committed to deliver products and services of world class standards and quality.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Technology</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our commitment to quality is reflected on our investment in process automation, research &amp; development, quality control equipment and machinery to enable the group to meet and seatisfy the product''s requirement.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">R &amp; D</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In line with our compony policy, we are constantly investing in R&amp;D equipment in order to carry out specialised quality test and evaluations of immediate and finished products.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Services</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">At SKP, we believe there is no substitute for personal service. Thus our team of dedicated and experience engineers are constantly upgrading themselves to provide you with the latest technical know-how, consultation (i.e., V.A. Analysis) engineering to your specifi</span></p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></div>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I began my career as a Sales executive. I decided to join SKP because of the company&rsquo;s excellent industry reputation, the career opportunities that exist, and the strong support sales people receive from the headquarters employees.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Sinkwang%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="273" height="350" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Copyright: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/profile_wavebreakmediamicro">wavebreakmediamicro / 123RF Stock Photo</a></p>', 'http://www.skpres.com/', 1, 0, 5, 333, '2014-05-25 11:00:55', '2014-06-20 14:23:04'),
(97, 3312, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/First%20engineering%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.3786267768255!2d103.80799999999998!3d1.539249999999992!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6c1197d08e37%3A0x94c4b015faffffae!2sFirst+Engineering+Plastics+(Malaysia)+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1402198163757" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">F</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">irst Engineering Limited is a leading manufacturer of ultra precision moulds and plastic components for high technology engineering applications. With operations in Singapore, Malaysia, China and India, we have a staff strength of over 2500 regionally with 800,000 sq ft of manufacturing space.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img style="display: block;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/First%20engineering%20cover%20values1.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="210" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Vision is to be the first choice global precision ENGINEERING Solutions provider. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Mission is to be the Preferred Supplier to our Customers, Employer to our Employees and Investment partner to our Shareholders.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/First%20engineering%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="611" height="466" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:http://www.first-engr.com/index.html</p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">At First Engineering, we offer our employees challenging and rewarding careers as we continuously identify and develop aspiring and dynamic individuals to join our talent pool. First Engineering'