(101, 3007, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Broadlandn%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.394400545894!2d103.815096!3d1.5307940000000038!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6c739cccfa77%3A0x93621d93317479b8!2sBroadland+Garment+Industries+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1404028288553" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Broadland Garment have operation in 3 different countries in Asia, that are Malaysia, Cambodia and China with his head office in Johor Jaya with a total factories area of about 220,000 sq. feet in 3 countries. Currently there are about a total of 2200 personnel working under it. The company is capable of export capacity of a total of 100,000 dozens of garment per month.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/broadland%20values2.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="250" /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To be Firm and Focus:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Broadland has always applied this principle whether it is making a minor or major decision. This has given clear direction to its workers in goal-achieving, thus avoiding carelessness, wastage of time and material in a labour-intensive industrial environment.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To Progress Prudently:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Broadland believes and practices gradual progression to enable its workforce to understand new procedures better, giving them time to equip and prepare themselves to achieve greater heights.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Financially, gradual progression will prevent the company from being dragged down through heavy bank repayments. This places the Company in constant solid financial standing.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To be Goal-Driven:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Broadland workforce mindset is focused and sharp, being goal-driven. The workforce will not be distracted to perform aimless, unplanned and non-value added efforts.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To Value the Human Asset:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Broadland is very focused on staff training. Its prerogative is to ensure that its staff is constantly kept abreast of the latest in new technologies and the development of new skills for higher productivity. It attributes its success to its hard-working staff. The Company''s attitude and efforts thus have earned the loyalty of the staff. This has in turn&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.broadland.com.my/index.asp</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/broadland%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="390" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Copyright: <a href="http://www.123rf.com/profile_kzenon">kzenon / 123RF Stock Photo</a>, http://www.broadland.com.my/index.asp</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I really enjoy working for Broadland Garment because I''m able to participate in many interesting and exciting projects while having fun and doing what I''m good at.I enjoy the strong bond between team members and the willingness of senior people to work with new employees in a supportive manner.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/broadland%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Copyright: 