(102, 3053, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/mnpl%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3988.385354679743!2d103.781725!3d1.535649!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xfa8cd72a87e22bd0!2sMNPL+Aluminium+Centre+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1406004739029" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">MNPL strives to increase productivity and reduce manufacturing/ fabrication costs for our customers by providing high quality and excellent machineability materials for the most demanding manufacturing and process applications.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In addition to our warehouse and cutting facilities in Singapore, MNPL group has warehouses with cutting facilities in Malaysia (MNPL Aluminium Centre Sdn. Bhd.) and China (MNPL Metals Co., Ltd.) as well. With our wide network of locations, MNPL group is able to cater to the regional needs of our valuable customers</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 150px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/mnpl%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="203" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our principal activities are the import and export of non-ferrous metals; and the operation of metal service centres, specializing in aluminium alloys (2024, 5052, 5083, 6061, 7075, MIC-6 plates, sheets, rods and bars). MNPL holds an inventory of about 1,000 metric tons in our factory which is available to our customers who wish to cut to size and to close tolerances.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;">Aluminum alloy products and components are used worldwide in the following industries:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span s