(108, 3244, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/TTMC%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3988.3785369899556!2d103.62231100000001!3d1.5392979999999998!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da7412286ac257%3A0x5e7c469e92809226!2sTTMC+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1408687436326" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">TTMC group is a company specializing in Welding &amp; Cutting equipments, distributing, automation series, trading and servicing business. We have been established for more than 15 years in Malaysia.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We aim to be the major Reliable player in the Welding, Cutting &amp; Automation Industry that provides Excellent Products Quality, Services &amp; Solutions Provider.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/TTMC%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="320" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:&nbsp;ttmcwelding.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">As one of the major Reliable player in the Welding, Cutting &amp; Automation Industry, we are hiring Fast! Interested candidate kindly send your resume via Godzilink.com</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.ttmcwelding.com/usr/page.aspx?pgid=2', 1, 0, 10, 603, '2014-08-22 14:13:38', '2014-11-16 13:11:59'),
(109, 1818, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/everspark%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3988.2189533803994!2d103.650674!3d1.6223689999999997!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da70a71418a89d%3A0x630129e7f24a84d0!2sEverspark+Industries+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1408952934522" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">At Everspark quality is a top priority. All units are given a thorough revamp and specific measures are in place to ensure that the only products we ship are those of impeccable quality. We meet these high standards with the help of our implementation of ISO 9001:2008. This uncompromising approach to quality has not only ensured the reliability and durability of our products, but has also made Everspark a well- respected name in the auto electrical component manufacturing market.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/everspark%20values.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="120" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: everspark.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/everspark%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="380" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: everspark.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/everspark%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="380" height="260" /></p>', 'http://www.everspark.com/home', 1, 0, 4, 906, '2014-08-25 16:01:17', '2014-11-02 10:03:13'),
(110, 2536, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/ttp%20fab%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.4505896928295!2d103.86724300000002!3d1.5002850000000032!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6ae2826a51b5%3A0xd3fffc4222bb4752!2sTTP+Fabricators+Sdn.+Bhd.+(478057-D)!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1410590465725" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">TTP engage in the activities such as procurement, construction,commissioning, project management, architectural and furnishing for living quarters, steel structure fabrication of topsides, jackets, decks, modules, and caisson pipes, small tripods, landing/handrails, helidecks,and structural skids for various types of production equipment. TTP also provide full EPCC services for modular accommodation cabins and other portable types of cabins.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/TTP%20fabrication%20value.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="400" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With three fabrication workshops and offices situated over East and West Malaysia, TTP is able to tackle on a variety of projects which include:</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Construction and Architectural works and Furnishing for living&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">quarters for offshore oil platform and marine vessels</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Modular cabins and other portable type such as laboratory, Co2 house,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">e-house, portable cold rooms etc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Above and underground piping works</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Mechanical equipment installation</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Refurnishment, modification, fabrication and erection of steel stucture&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">and equipment</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/TTP%20fabrication%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="570" height="330" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are proud to&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px;">design world class products with great people in a great environment</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">and &amp; process excellence that are driven by our strong values. We are a market leader because we help our customers succeed in their business.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/synthomer%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '', 1, 0, 32, 676, '2014-09-13 14:54:49', '2014-11-23 13:14:04'),
(111, 3546, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/vermi%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3988.117373280846!2d103.55199999999999!3d1.6730999999999998!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da788435e57b9b%3A0xc10ba2088c7787b4!2sVermi+Industries+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1411270331370" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">It is always our first priority to ensure the safety and wholesome of our products for customers consumption. Therefore, all of our products are under the Singapore&rsquo;s AVA stringent food safety standards and regulations.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/vermi%20values.jpg" alt="" width="516" height="90" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;">HACCP Specification MI-H02, the quality management system and HACCP system is applicable to Production (polishing, mixing, extruding, cooking and drying) of rice vermicelli (mee hoon), packed in plastic bag.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">VERMI INDUSTRIES SDN BHD has been assessed and found compliant with the requirement of ISO 9001: 2008 / BS EN ISO 9001: 2008</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/vermi%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="305" height="365" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo coyright:vermi.com.my</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">If you are looking for a career in food industries, to captialize your management and technical skills, here is a good chance!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;">Join our team now</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.vermi.com.my/', 1, 0, 4, 548, '2014-09-21 11:46:29', '2014-12-12 17:39:03');
