(112, 3310, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bika%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1994.258479118211!2d103.755!3d1.4634300000000113!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da12c6d5f91661%3A0x1da16860197cf3b4!2sHua+Huat+Manufacturing+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1412580658869" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Precision</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">It is vital not to miss a single step in overall processing. Our quality department stress on every quality control point, which includes inspection on every batch of products from raw materials to finished goods. We are actively involved in research &amp; development to improve current products and also to develop new products to better reflect market trends and demand.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Your Concern</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We understand that hygiene and food safety is very important to you. Therefore it is what we care most in our production processes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Freshness</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We pack every quality assured pieces in time to ensure the freshness when you take the first bite.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bika%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="510" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photocopyright: bika.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are actively searching for potential talents to join us &amp; grow our business venture globally.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">If you have the skills,experiences that meet our requirements, come and apply now!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'www.bika.com.my', 1, 0, 1, 563, '2014-10-06 15:45:45', '2014-11-02 10:01:20'),
(113, 3110, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/HBGlass%20and%20aluminium.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.4419871614714!2d103.72731099999999!3d1.5049959999999925!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da729cebbd4cc7%3A0x802529d6244e2fc2!2sHui+Beng+Glass+%26+Aluminium+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1412582269260" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company plays a leading role in the architecture of awesome skyscrapers as well as internationally-acknowledge hotels and resorts. Capturing the imagination and inspiration of our audience, our glass panels, panes and other fine sculptures clearly reflect sophistication and elegance. The demands of architects and consultants grow increasingly exciting, we have made it our commitment to deliver what the industry request and requires.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Aluminium Doors</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Sliding doors, Swing doors, Entrance doors, Automatic sliding doors, Curve sliding doors, Louvres doors &amp; Frameless glass doors.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Aluminium Windows</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Sliding windows, Casement windows, Side hung, Top hung, Bottom hung, Pivoted windows &amp; Lourve windows</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Others Products</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Skylights, Shopfront, Fire-rated roller shutters (1-2 hours), Partitions, Suspended ceiling, Suspended glass system &amp; frameless glass system</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/HBGlass%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="320" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:http://www.hbaluminium.com</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We want you to innovate, to lead, to aspire. We rely on those qualities to make us who we are: a company that accomplishes great things and is a leader in the Glass &amp; Aluminium industry.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'http://www.hbaluminium.com/usr/page.aspx?pgid=1', 1, 0, 2, 769, '2014-10-06 16:10:53', '2014-12-26 12:25:33'),
(114, 3702, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/sds%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.3676502414164!2d103.69336399999997!3d1.545107000000009!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da722f91ea8767%3A0x8f6f20121a0b9193!2sSDS+Food+Manufacturing+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1413598950504" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We have been training our management staffs how to manage, as well as our employees how to take care of their jobs. Good management and trained personnel are the most important factors in our career &amp; business.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Good personnel will work for a competent manager. We go every length to find, hire, and train good employees and treat them like our family. This is the crux of our whole operation in SDS group.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Todays, SDS Groups has holding TOP BAKER and SDS CLASSIC as its subsidiary. Where TOP BAKER focus on wholesaling of bakery products local and internationally. SDS Classic building a Europe style of bakery and cafeteria into Malaysia market.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sds%20cover.jpg" alt="" width="602" height="210" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:sdsgroup.com</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/SDS%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="599" height="500" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:sdsgroup.com</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">SDS is a recognized, food industry-leading company. I''m proud to work for SDS for these reasons, but I''m mostly proud because SDS cares about its people and is committed to the success of its employees</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/sds%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="260" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'http://www.sdsgroups.com/', 1, 0, 7, 946, '2014-10-18 10:39:29', '2014-11-16 13:12:22'),
(115, 3551, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/miroad%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.220520348641!2d103.656162!3d1.6215740000000034!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da70a3074b649b%3A0x9a99ba28095cf816!2sMiroad+Rubber+Industries+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1414304410561" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In 2006, Rubber Tiles production was added to production line. As a leading manufacturer with support of dynamic and experienced workforce, Miroad has been growing rapidly and products are marketed globally with quality and delivery assurance.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Once rubber waste is destined to landfills, scrap tyres and recyclable rubbers will be shredded and processed into small granules. Our manufacturing experts will mix, mould &amp; transform these granules into rubber tiles.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/miroad%20values.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:miroadrubber.com</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/miroad%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="390" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:miroad.com</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/miroad%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="240" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Miroad recognizes the importance of new product development and believes in the ingenuity of its employees. In this role, we are afforded a creative and diverse environment to work closely with the talented specialists in different departments from around Malaysia.</span></p>', 'http://www.miroadrubber.com/index.htm', 1, 0, 13, 517, '2014-10-26 14:34:05', '2014-12-26 12:24:45'),
(116, 3596, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/henghiap%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.4530881448236!2d103.844684!3d1.4989140000000019!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6b14cda838b1%3A0x21fdd763868a7173!2sHeng+Hiap+Industries+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1414306075963" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #808080;">10 years of plastics re-engineering in producing smart plastics material from plastics scrap</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #808080;">Heng Hiap is a fully integrated recycling company in Malaysia and we strategically located in Johor Bahru. We strongly believes in the value of scrap as a renewable resource.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><strong>Corporate Goals &amp; Strategies</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Strive for sustainable growth and financial sustainability</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Develop and customize for the Niche Market</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Diversify business portfolio</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Improve Core Competencies</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Maximize Resources, minimize wastes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Integration through strategic ISO implementation</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/henghiap%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="619" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #999999;">photo copyright:henghiap.com</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/henghiap%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">On behalf of our team here we wanted to recognize the value that Henghiap Group brings to our industries. From the pick-up drivers to the support staff our team always partners with us to make sure our needs are met. Our team is always flexible and offers options that make it easy for us to do business together. We consistently communicate any changes in schedule and is always willing to meet last minute needs. Providing our company with a way to recycle the wide variety of product, we have help our industries with wide green initiative. Thanks again!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #999999;">photo coyright:henghiap.com</span></p>', 'http://www.henghiap.com/hh_WEB/index.html', 1, 0, 11, 577, '2014-10-26 15:03:54', '2015-01-18 04:07:41'),
