(118, 3564, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/TGMF%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3988.5051942495656!2d103.923!3d1.47003!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da3ffbb294f7cd%3A0x5fa48bed8a0a7164!2sTeck+%26+Guan+Metal+Finishing+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1414896190109" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our staff of highly trained engineers and operators posses over 100 years of combined experience and our process control is continuously improved on every day. Our selective electroplating systems reduce the consumption of precious metals and high speed processing make us the most competitive metal finishing shop in South of Peninsular Malaysia. We rally around challenging metal plating opportunities and support our services with a World Class organization that delivers on our promise, Impeccable Service.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/teck%20n%20guan%20metal.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="320" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:tgmf.com.my</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I have found TGMF to be a place where hard work is recognized and the possibility of promotion is available to everyone. There is more opportunity than there are good leaders. I personally like being a part of a company that has people with strong moral values.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/tgmf%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="277" height="241" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:tgmf.com.my</span></p>', 'http://www.tgmf.com.my/index.html', 1, 0, 5, 342, '2014-11-02 10:48:13', '2014-12-12 17:38:42'),
(119, 3998, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bi%20technologies%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1990.4963202186889!2d103.33952834101119!3d3.811669574261604!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31c8babccc01afb3%3A0xb655b0f690ce7d1a!2sBi+Technologies+Corporation+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1417318933014" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Vision and Values</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our vision is to be the preferred and most trusted provider of performance-critical technology solutions to world-leading manufacturers, embedding innovation in everything we do.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We promise to develop pioneering electronic solutions and consistently, provide an excellent, competitive experience for all who come into contact with TT Electronics.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our six core values are our foundation:</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bi%20technologies%20values1.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="110" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our behavioural principles help us achieve our vision. We believe we can</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bi%20technologies%20values2(1).jpg" alt="" width="535" height="170" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Across the divisions, we have hundreds of specialist experts and a focus on key markets, enabling us to provide a comprehensive range of advanced technology, application specific engineered solutions and innovative products. All supported by world-class manufacturing facilities and application engineering teams</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Bi%20technologies%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="344" height="608" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #999999;">photo copyright:http://www.ttelectronics.com/en</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">A career at TT Electronics is your opportunity to help shape the future of electronics. To add your skills to a dynamic, innovative team of professionals. To be part of a company that&rsquo;s recognised the world over for delivering technologies that transform our everyday lives. Come and join a diverse, global community where you can partner with great minds and inspiring people. And be part of a business backed by the financial strength that drives growth &ndash; and career opportunities</span></p>', 'http://www.ttelectronics.com/en', 1, 0, 7, 341, '2014-11-30 11:44:12', '2015-01-18 03:28:42'),
(120, 3982, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/afamosa%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3986.185850617686!2d102.218226!3d2.4450909999999992!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31ce0302f1b56793%3A0xe5b90d24c3288c87!2sA&#39;famosa+Water+World!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1417319533884" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Spanning a 520-hectare site, A''Famosa Resort is a one stop venue for business and leisure. It boasts a 27-holes international Golf Course, Water World, Safari World, Old West, Resort hotel</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/afamosa%20values.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="190" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #999999;">photo copyright:afamosa.com</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/afamosa%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="530" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">A&rsquo;Famosa Resort provides you with boundless opportunities in a multi-disciplined environment.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are pleased to provide a listing of our current career opportunities in various segments of operations, Sales, management and administrative roles&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Are you up to the challenge?&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Come and experience a new way of living and working. We look forward to meeting you!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/afamosa%20testimonial.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="210" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #999999;">photo copyright:afamosa.com</span></p>', 'http://www.afamosa.com/', 1, 0, 1, 288, '2014-11-30 12:07:17', '2015-01-18 03:28:13