(121, 4195, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/PIE%20eratech%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.3557950745103!2d103.82416800000006!3d1.5514080000000003!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6bfe34b2d94b%3A0xbf92bab16bbc5443!2sJalan+Mahir+2%2C+Taman+Perindustrian+Cemerlang%2C+81800+Ulu+Tiram%2C+Johor!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1419567311422" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company philosophy is providing engineering solution for all kinds of product manufacturing and production.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The principle business included design, fabrication, machining, assembly, testing and installation of designed jigs, fixtures and semi-automated equipment. Besides, the company also support for new products&rsquo; raw parts machining and modification during engineering build and start-up.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our Facilities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">CNC Miling Machines,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Conventional Miling Machines,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Lathe Machines,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Table Lathe Machines,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Surface Grinding Machines,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Centerless Grinding Machines</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/PIE%20eratech%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="425" height="410" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">P.I.E. Eratech Sdn Bhd offer opportunities for career advancement and professional development. Our team-based approach also provides room to pursue personal visions of e