(122, 4125, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/GWI%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.3546599028646!2d103.82300000000001!3d1.5520100000000014!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da6bffdfa9b5ab%3A0x4a8c3089e2cde577!2sGWI+Manufacturing+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1419568152905" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">GWI&rsquo;s in-depth knowledge in Vacuum Thermoforming grew with nearly 3 decades of support from a wide spectrum of customers. We have the competitive edge to have both the experiences of a manufacturer of packaging products, as well as being a user of packaging products (being the Packaging Service Provider).</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With the above experiences, we are able to provide customers with best designs with considerations on the technical requirement during packaging processes. Recommendations on the most suitable material and providing all technical inputs required. Consistent quality and competitive pricing has always been our key elements in building long term relationships with our customers.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With facilities in Singapore, Malaysia and China, we are confident to meet all your packaging needs for the whole Asia-Pacific region.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our wide spectrum of customers includes those from the high end Hard-Disk Drive Industry, Electronics Industry, Medical Equipment and Products Industry, Food and Consumer Products Packaging</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/GWI%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="295" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Its exciting to be part of a growing office that provides you the opportunity to collaborate with people from different industries. Working with us is a chance to innovate for good.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.gwip.com.my/default2.htm', 1, 0, 7, 444, '2014-12-26 12:51:01', '2015-03-14 17:07:33'),
(123, 4221, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Omron%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3984.0174268359547!2d101.61044500000001!3d3.090019!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc4c71531f6269%3A0x45ef8aa79584e540!2sOmron+Malaysia+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1421524807004" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">OMRON''s operations are guided by our vision and philosophy, as expressed in the OMRON Principles, which function as corporate ethics guidelines, and our corporate statement, "Sensing Tomorrow."</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In addition to these guiding values, our approach to business is shaped by the SINIC theory developed by OMRON founder Kazuma Tateisi and by our view of the "ideal" society.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The SINIC theory - a future prediction theory developed by OMRON founder Kazuma Tateisi in 1970 - is the compass that guides OMRON''s management. Using the SINIC theory, OMRON has successfully anticipated and responded to societal needs, drawing on our proprietary sensing and control technology to produce products and services that contribute to society.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<div style="padding-left: 120px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Omron%20values.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="300" /></div>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/omron%20gallery1.jpg" alt="" width="530" height="502" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:www.omron.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">OMRON''s employees benefit society by roactively sensing the needs of people and rapidly creating solutions to meet those needs</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.omron.com/', 1, 0, 11, 274, '2015-01-18 04:07:45', '2015-03-08 14:36:36'),
(124, 4124, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/success%20transformer%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3983.7340131323454!2d101.57222900000001!3d3.1646220000000005!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc4f07f40dd80f%3A0x9478bb0a365745b4!2sSuccess+Electronics+%26+Transformer+Manufacturer+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1421525437456" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">SETM is wholly owned by Success Transformer Corporation Berhad, which is the first company of its kind to be listed on the Main Board of Malaysia&rsquo;s securities exchange, Bursa Malaysia.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We provide the most comprehensive range of low voltage transformers in Malaysia. We also supply a large volume of industrial lighting to both domestic and international markets.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The consistently high standard of our work has engendered a loyal and longstanding customer base. It has also led to an increase in new business both domestically and overseas.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We have a committed and dynamic workforce. From management through technical and Research &amp; Development (R&amp;D) engineers to sales and support staff, we all work as one team with the same goal in mind: customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/success%20transformer%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="341" height="582" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:success.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/success%20transformer%20values.jpg" alt="" width="258" height="173" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I work with such a great group of people that it makes it fun to come to work every day. I also enjoy the challenge of accounting for the new products and programs - it never gets boring.. I appreciate that recognition is given when it''s deserved, and help offered when needed.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.success.com.my/index.php', 1, 0, 6, 231, '2015-01-18 04:42:04', '2015-02-15 10:01:16'),
(125, 4111, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Elemac%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3986.6861809057145!2d102.228!3d2.27044!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31d1faeb3c076867%3A0xd3bbeb199e09b880!2sElemac+Engineering+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1421528335674" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are the precision machine parts supplier to numbers of well-known machine maker both in local and oversea.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our business cover industries like semiconductor, automation, optical, medical and aerospace. In addition, beside fabrication business we produce machine frame structure and also assembling sub-module for machines maker with the Built-Of-Material(BOM) provided from our customers and we also provide with one-stop-solution services.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Elemac%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="500" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:http://www.elemac.com.my/index.html</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Whether you''re fresh out of college, or an experienced professional, Elemac is a company where you can cultivate your expertise, use your knowledge to the fullest extent</span></p>', 'http://www.elemac.com.my/index.html', 1, 0, 8, 233, '2015-01-18 05:05:08', '2015-02-15 10:16:15'),
(126, 4044, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/boarding%20engineering%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1992.4156028249874!2d101.81197268637021!3d2.8650420218660595!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cdc5ee46c97f3d%3A0x25f79ec6697bfd18!2sJalan+Permata+1%2F1%2C+Kawasan+Perindustrian+Nilai%2C+71800+Nilai%2C+Negeri+Sembilan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1421529039128" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With collaboration with our associate companies and oversea partners, we specialized in Engineering system solution provider. Our works involve in design, fabrication, installation and maintenance works for foundry industries and extend to chemical, automotive, steel mills, power plant, cement, food and aerospace related industry. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We also do hold products distributorship for various well known international brand. We have established long term relationship with Sintokogio, Japan, a world class foundry equipment manufacturer since 1997 to provide sales and service activities for their full range of products.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/boarding%20engineering%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="468" height="426" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:www.be.com.my</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The entire team works towards the goal of making our products better and there is little conflict. This atmosphere starts at the top levels of the company. When you have that mentality at the top, it can&rsquo;t help but affect every aspect of the company. I would say my greatest achievement is looking back at projects I&rsquo;ve done in the past</span></p>', 'http://www.be.com.my/index.shtml', 1, 0, 9, 183, '2015-01-18 05:30:14', '2015-02-15 10:32:22'),
(127, 4282, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/dickson%20marine%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3985.832955244769!2d101.81555999999999!3d2.561128!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cdf1e18264e4c1%3A0xd4ba0aff230819d9!2sDickson+Marine+Company+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1421531054686" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Dickson Marine Co. has been involved in petroleum trading activities since 1985. The company was established by its beloved founder the late Tn. Syed Abdul Bahari bin Syed Abdullah Al-Haj.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In 1996, the company was incorporated into Dickson Marine Co. Sdn Bhd. &nbsp;Since then the group has grown consistently over the years.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To date the Group has a total workforce of 70 staff consisting of professionals, managers, administration staff and skilled workers. The Group &nbsp;has a combined paid up of &nbsp;RM3.5 million and net assets worth RM17 million.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The key spirit of our Group is &nbsp;TEAMWORK and management values and recognizes the contribution of every staff within the group.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/dickson%20marine%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="518" height="330" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.dmcgroup.com.my/</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We value deep expertise from experienced professionals to support our growing company. Consider these opportunities if you are ready to apply your knowledge and expertise.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.dmcgroup.com.my/', 1, 0, 1, 320, '2015-01-18 05:49:36', '2015-03-08 13:41:34'),
(128, 4526, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/ECT%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.37365811028!2d103.63308599999999!3d1.5419040000000028!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da7408f94b77f3%3A0x69f399ba669a8367!2sEuro-Circuit+Technology+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1423966226443" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">ECT is expanding into a new business segment of blending and producing water based and biodegradable cleaning chemical. ECT choose this new branch of business due to human needs for cleanliness and hygiene in all aspects of modern life be it personal, society and industries. In line with the governments campaign and vision of turning Malaysia into one of the garden cities.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">ECT is directly linked up with experts from the research and professional institutions at national and international levels. Our goal is not simply to provide superb service but also to build solid relationships with people who share our commitment in providing a green solution for the nation.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">ECT&rsquo;s exclusive environmental focus is backed by a team of highly motivated professionals who take pride in constantly exceeding expectations. Allow us to show you that we can work in partnership together to resolve the environmental concern.</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">ENVIRONMENTAL CONSULTANCY</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Environmental engineering studies</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Waste management</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Industrial Waste Water Monitoring</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; EIA Plantation</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; EIA Township</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Environmental Management Plan (EMP)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">TECHNOLOGY CONSULTANCY</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Metallurgy and Materials Technology</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Environmental Planning</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Development and Project Management</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Cleaning Services</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; Oil Spill</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; Solid Waste</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; Building</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&gt; Oil &amp; Gas Industries</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">PRODUCTS</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- BIO-SOLV (Biodegradable Water Based Oil Dispersant)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- CDM AVS (Clean Development Mechanism AVS System under Kyoto Protocol)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- MERUS (Corrosion Inhibitor &amp; Descaling of Piping System)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Coal for Power Generation</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- 100% Organic Arabica Coffee (Acheh)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- Drinking Water Treatment Plant</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">(Chemical, Filtration &amp; Membrane Technology, Reverse Osmosis)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">* We design and custom made to specified requirement.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">- GEOGRIT Road System</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We have done an excellent job of maintaining compliance with new environmental laws and regulations. We have been proactive and are one step ahead of any visits from environmental agencies. We would like to invite potential candidates to apply for our vacancies and make our country a better place.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://euro-circuit.blogspot.com/', 1, 0, 6, 496, '2015-02-15 10:15:13', '2015-05-17 13:27:23'),
(129, 2958, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/eurojaya%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3986.7172437230747!2d102.228044!3d2.259152!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31d1fa99c48a37dd%3A0x9a7c1acec9e2f26a!2sEUROJAYA+PRECISION+SDN+BHD!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1423967293010" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">We are certified by ISO 9001:2008 Quality Management System. Our experienced and highly skilled personnel in machining techniques are capable of producing high quality tools that meet the standard precision requirements of multinational companies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">We believe that the path of success in business is through sincerity, commitment and mutual understanding. As customer satisfaction is our highest priority, we are constantly focusing on improving the quality of our services by developing new manufacturing technologies to help improve the quality of products, productivity and efficiency</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Initially Eurojaya was established to provide tungsten carbide grinding service, producing punches and dies of profile, down-set, comb and forming for leadframe, connector stamping and semiconductor industries.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/eurojaya%20values.jpg" style="height:160px; width:406px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>photo copyright: eurojaya.com.my</p>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:11pt">Our Core Business:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Manufacture of Precision Tools &amp; Dies,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">High-Speed Metal Stamping Tools and</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Metal Fabrication for Electronics &amp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Manufacturing Industries.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:11pt">Speciality:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Punches, Dies, &nbsp;Mould parts, &nbsp;Gauges, Jig &amp; Fixtures&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Design and fabrication of cutting tools</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Material: Tungsten Carbide, Tools Steel, SUS,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Aluminium, All Plastic &amp; Polymer, other</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Custom Job shop Machine parts design by client</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:11pt">Our technical team capabilities:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Achieving tolerance up to 0.002mm accuracy</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Super drilling (hole up to 0.10 mm diameter)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">On time project delivery</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Prompt customer reply- technical and quote.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/eurojaya%20gallery.jpg" style="height:175px; width:487px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>photo copyright: surojaya.com.my</p>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">&nbsp;At Eurojaya, developmental opportunities are readily available through on-the-job experiences, stretch assignments, projects, training and mentoring, and I have taken advantage of all these.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'http://www.eurojaya.com.my/', 1, 0, 8, 684, '2015-02-15 10:30:48', '2015-09-02 16:52:21'),
(130, 4531, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/Joven.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3984.3547125922573!2d101.499702!3d2.99882!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cdac920d257599%3A0x6844b0c23b594fe8!2sJoven+Electric+Co.+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1423968578245" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Joven owns a factory of 118,000 Sq ft. employing over 100 staffs and have a production capacity of over 150,000 pieces a year. Joven began competing in various categories for its brand name and manufacturing standards. Joven have been awarded the Brand Excellence Award 2009, Special Award for Innovative Design 2009, Industrial Excellence Award 2009 by MITI and the Malaysian Good Design Mark by the Malaysian Design Council back in 2009 and 2000.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"> In year 2002, Joven was certified by the Water Quality Association and Joven is also awarded ISO 9001 Mark for its quality management system in manufacturing. In year 2005, Joven was awarded the Malaysia Superbrands Award for its recognition of its brand name among Malaysian consumers</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/Joven%20values.jpg" alt="" width="485" height="244" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright:joven-electric.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/joven%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="490" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: joven-electric.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I have been with Joven for 6 years. I take pride in the many achievements I&rsquo;ve had at Joven and I enjoy working with my co workers and also learning about new technologies. This is an easy going group of people who will help you learn as you go. Joven also makes strides to care about us as individuals.</span></p>', 'http://www.joven-electric.com/index.php', 1, 0, 23, 294, '2015-02-15 10:53:15', '2015-04-19 13:26:59'),
(131, 4541, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/central%20cables%20berhad%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3986.796446154891!2d102.26153599999999!3d2.2301119999999997!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31d1effe6963df1d%3A0x7e382356b99743e1!2sCentral+Cables+Berhad!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1423969096721" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We specialises in the manufacture of power cables of copper and aluminium from 1kV to 33kV. Our range of products also cater for housing wires. Central Cables Berhad also supply wide range of telecommunication cables and special cables for oil &amp; gas and marine cable.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Always provide quality&rsquo;s products and services at competitive price that consistently meet Customer Satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">All employees strive for excellent in Quality, Productivity and Service by complying to ISO 9001:2000 requirements.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">To ensure Continuous Improvement.</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">CCB supplies cables required by Tenaga Nasional Berhad (TNB), the largest electricity utility in Malaysia, Syarikat SESCO Berhad (formerly known as Sarawak Electricity Supply Corporation), Sabah Electricity Sdn. Bhd. (SESB), Jabatan Kerja Raya (JKR - the Public Works Department of Malaysia) and private sector clients. CCB&rsquo;s export market includes Mauritius, Philippines, Indonesia, Singapore, Australia, Vietnam, Ghana, Zimbabwe and Myanmar.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/central%20cables%20berhad%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="279" height="548" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>photo copyright: central-cables.com</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I decided to join central cables because of the company&rsquo;s excellent industry reputation, the career opportunities that exist, and the strong support from organization</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.central-cables.com/html/about.html', 1, 0, 25, 233, '2015-02-15 11:09:59', '2015-04-05 13:24:06');
