(148, 5056, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/dover%20elevator%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3983.8081678907033!2d101.71589999999999!3d3.1452730000000004!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc362e67c0f1ab%3A0x617ae9a568542529!2sDover+Elevators+(Malaysia)+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1433962292102" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0">', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Dover Elevator Systems Inc., USA, was a division of Dover Corporation USA which had operating divisions in industries such as defence/aerospace, communications, electronics, vapor recovery, etc.Owing to globalization and to increase the competitiveness, many multinational companies seek and develop manufacturing facilities offshore closer to the point of sales. In this context, in 1998 Dover USA had started sourcing lift controllers and traction machines from original equipment manufacturers in Korea for its Asia Pacific market. Dover Elevators (Malaysia) Sdn Bhd inherited this practice and is still sourcing from the same original equipment manufacturer to Dover Elevator Systems Inc of USA.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.6666660308838px;">Dover Elevators (M) Sdn Bhd currently maintains over 1,000 units of lifts and escalators on service contract across Malaysia.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our products are Elevator, Escalator, passenger Conveyer</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/dover%20elevator%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="348" height="397" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.dover-elevators.com.my/</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are always looking for highly motivated personnel to join our team.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We offer a wide variety of benefits. Benefits include Health Insurance, Term Life Insurance, Transport &amp; Telephone allowances, yearly bonus and more</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.dover-elevators.com.my/index.html', 1, 1, 11, 210, '2015-06-11 02:59:39', '2015-07-11 11:51:38'),
(149, 5050, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/advance%20equipment%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3984.018004889895!2d101.63040199999999!3d3.089864999999999!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc4b93b1432887%3A0xcd957199e1842914!2sAdvanced+Equipment+(M)+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1433963254600" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0">', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Our continuing passion for application and cutting edge technologies allows us to create complete solutions that make our customers more productive and successful. We design and fabricate automatic systems for handling, picking, welding and cutting system.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Welding and Cutting</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Advanced Equipment (M) Sdn Bhd has been a distributor of Lincoln Electric since 1979. Based on our good understanding of welding process and years of experience, we provide the latest technology products and solutions.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Automation Solution</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">In the manufacturing industries, countless problems have arisen and will continue to emerge. Advanced Equipment (M) Sdn Bhd has been many years involved in these industries and are fully aware of these problems.With the increase benefits of robotics, robots give our customer the flexibility, cost savings and accuracy they search for. Vision systems are being integrated into robotic finishing cells to identify parts and to verify positioning. There is no need to arrange parts in a certain order. This reduces human work.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With technologies in our hand, we can develop automated equipment to the best for our customers need. Helping manufacturers to improve productivity and quality products using complete automated solutions designed to reduce labor, material costs and increase profitability.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We serve clients with our best of specialty and the best effort in these industries:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Automation,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Motorsports,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Constructions,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Oil and Gas on shore &amp; off shore,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Manufacturing,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Structural,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Fabrication,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Pipe Welding,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Food Industries,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Packaging,</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Palletizing Industries</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/advance%20equipment%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="526" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #888888;">photo copyright:&nbsp;http://www.advancedequipment.com.my/home.aspx?p=3</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14.6666660308838px;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">I appreciate that recognition is given when it''s deserved, and help offered when needed. I like that the support system is there from supervisors and colleagues, plus well-balanced with the freedom and autonomy they give us to be successful. I feel like I''ve been kept on track with the right amount of supervision. It''s a very well-rounded organization that manages to keep my job fulfilling and interesting and a pleasure to be doing everyday!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.advancedequipment.com.my/home.aspx?p=3', 1, 0, 3, 231, '2015-06-11 03:16:18', '2015-08-01 13:39:35'),
(150, 5032, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/chempro%20technology%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3984.40902903197!2d101.54786399999999!3d2.9838730000000004!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cdb2663ab0a5ad%3A0x62df6961472af126!2sChempro+Technology+(M)+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1433964605642" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0">', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Today, Chempro Technology''s commitment and capabilities are evident from the strategically placed operations all over Asia, in countries like Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia, Brunei, Hong Kong, Taiwan and China.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">With a combined workforce of over 600 specialists, Chempro Technology is also actively pursuing research and development to continuously provide world-class services and products at the most competitive cost for optimum results.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Building on such solid foundation, Chempro Technology is well poised to spearhead Asia''s leading role in the global industrial chemical market.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Through extensive research and development we innovate new products to meet the ever-changing needs of clients from different sectors.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;Instituitional, Water treatment, Food &amp; Industrial</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/chempro%20tech%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="445" height="544" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;">photo copyright:http://www.chempro.com.my/en/main.html</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #888888;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Chempro Technology has been at the forefront