(152, 5216, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/travelite%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3984.255556511633!2d101.6051128!3d3.0259158999999998!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cdb350175daad5%3A0x39eb3dd98bee50f3!2sTravelite+Marketing+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1436585597594" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" ', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The leading lifestyle brand management company in Asia and key international markets.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Enhance shareholders&rsquo; value through a continued focus on profitability</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Increase consumer loyalty through excellent customer service</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Expand our brand representation &amp; product segments through strategic acquisitions, joint ventures or alliances</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The brands we represent</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/travelite%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="450" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">We are constantly on the lookout for Sales Executives/Associates with go-getter mentality and great service attitude. Contact us if you have the right qualities to make a significant contribution to the team!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.etravelite.com/', 1, 1, 1, 3, '2015-07-11 11:51:19', '2015-07-11 11:51:19'),
(153, 5214, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/SAQ%20builder%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3983.8774976252616!2d101.6455098!3d3.1270748!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc496ea2309915%3A0x1425827c99c66204!2sSqa+Builders+Sdn+Bhd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1436587340825" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">SQA Builders Sdn Bhd (SQA) is a progressive Malaysian Japanese contractor. It is part of the SQA Group, established in 1997. Our competitive advantage is our ability to provide a wide range of construction and renovation services to our clients with "Speed" and "Quality" "Assurance" hence forming the name of our company. SQA has also been recognised as a respected turnkey contractor on a number of projects. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">SQA works closely with its subsidiaries, SQA Corporation Sdn Bhd and Well Assist Corporation Sdn Bhd which consolidate our position in the construction and building material supply market. The SQA Group also engages in property development activities through its subsidiary and has an excellent track record in building high quality shop offices, showrooms, factory warehouses, bungalows, condominiums, and institutional buildings.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Some of our completed projects</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/SQA%20builder%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="399" height="576" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Working on a goal oriented, mix international team where people share the sheer enthusiasm to work for a company that plays a key role in the construction markets.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.sqa.com.my/', 1, 1, 9, 115, '2015-07-11 12:15:12', '2015-07-11 12:16:14'),
(154, 5162, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/stanta%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3984.11105367038!2d101.47966!3d3.064975!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc530163120871%3A0xb8bd6363f583af00!2sStanta+Mauser+(M)+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1436588294984" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The MAUSER Group is a leading producer of industrial packaging with almost 4,000 employees and consolidated revenues of 1 billion Euros. The MAUSER Group operates more than 50 production facilities across Europe, North America, Latin America and Asia. Two licensing networks &ndash; one for plastic packaging and one for the production of steel drums &ndash; include approximately 30 members in more than 20 countries that make MAUSER quality products and services available worldwide.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Since its inception in 1975, Stanta Metal Drum Sdn. Bhd. has evolved to be the top metal drum manufacturer in Malaysia. The partnership between Stanta and Mauser aims to complement each other and will further increase the competitiveness of metal drum manufacturing globally.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/stanta%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="330" height="240" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Being part of the German-based Mauser Group as well as a leading producer of industrial packaging with 4,400 employees worldwide and revenues of EURO 1.2 billion, it has been STANTA MAUSER''s driving philosophy to provide quality product and services. In line with our expansion plan, we seek highly dynamic, motivated and dedicated individual to join our team.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.stantamauser.com/about.html', 1, 1, 10, 117, '2015-07-11 12:35:50', '2015-07-11 12:35:50'),
(155, 5237, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/lenmin%20steel%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3983.83822625088!2d101.62108029999997!3d3.137396000000004!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc4933f7ec7e79%3A0x7ca323c9595bd7db!2sLen+Min+Steel+Sdn.+Bhd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1438403006271" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Bonding the gap between the needs of contractors and building materials manufacturers for the growth of the construction industry and be an integral part of nation building by constantly sourcing for innovative quality products that leads to quality buildings and structures.To be the preferred building materials supplier in Peninsular Malaysia by setting up two branches one in the north and the other in the southern peninsular to provide close support to customer&rsquo;s projects.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/leemin%20steel%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="440" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Len Min Steel is a great place for young and creative minds to apply their skills and knowledge they possess and let their talent prosper in a positive working environment.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'http://www.lenminsteel.com/index.php', 1, 1, 3, 64, '2015-08-01 13:39:01', '2015-08-01 13:39:01'),
(156, 5230, '/webroot/upload/image/featured/optima%20window%20cover.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3983.5812312189714!2d101.59804299999999!3d3.204119!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc45edd27ca123%3A0xda001bcde87b2a1!2sOPTIMA+WINDOW+SDN+BHD!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smy!4v1438407712312" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">The company consists of professional consultants who work side by side with clients, ensuring that projects involving aluminium frames and glass windows and doors are executed and installed according to plan. Our service is reputable as we always place our customers'' needs before us and by doing our best to help clients achieve smooth execution of their projects.</span></p>', '<p><img src="/webroot/upload/image/featured/optima%20window%20gallery.jpg" alt="" width="492" height="491" /></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Quality work, great environment and learning opportunities are the reasons why we chose to work with Optima Windows. Our seniors and colleagues are very organized and easy to work with.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></p>', 'http://www.optimawindow.com/index.html', 1, 1, 14, 64, '2015-08-01 13:56:19', '2015-08-01 13:58:20');
