(2, 'PHO-2016-002', 48, 1, 0, 'Sampe Oppo A', '<p>Sample ABC</p>\r\n', 'Vix ei posse partem iisque. Idque regione eum ei, case propriae partiendo pri ex, natum nostro consequuntur at est. Has id feugait accusam, diam agam facilisis sea ut. Vel et solum fastidii officiis, quas illud invenire est at, id cum conceptam efficiendi contentiones. Ius ex aperiri consetetur. Vim ei alii eloquentiam, eius movet et nec.', 'Sample Requirements', 1, 1, 'Santa Rosa', '2017-07-27', 1, '', 1, 'test', '2016-11-18 04:29:06', '2016-11-18 04:32:34', 2000, 0, 0, '', 0, 0),
(7, 'AUO-2016-007', 19, 1, 1, 'Level 2/3 Systems Engineer', '<p><strong>Being specialist recruiters for Managed Service Providers, I was excited to receive yet another job, so had to share it with you MSP specialists...&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Fantastic company culture - mature, well defined</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A&nbsp;customer focussed MSP that does things properly</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Get valued for your technical skills</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>So this is a job for anyone with serious tech skills and IT company experience that enjoys looking after small and medium sized businesses doing both project and support work onsite or remotely. Ethics and a culture of excellence is absolutely key in this environment, so if you are prepared to go the extra mile for the client then this is the role for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Genuine Level 2/3 systems engineer role</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>MSP or similar time based billing environment experience</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Keenness to excel in a Managed Services</strong> <strong>Provider</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Attention to detail, doing a job well, and being on top of your game technically are all essential attributes for this role. You will need to have outstanding customer service communication skills be able to work in a team and have solid, broad tech skills. If you work for or have worked for a Managed Services Provider or IT company looking after small and medium sized businesses then you are in the box seat for this role.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reasonable support experience with the following technologies are needed or desired&ndash;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Desktops in AD environments</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Server 2003 - 2012</strong> -<strong> admin/install experience</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Small Business Server 2003/2008/2011 - install/admin</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exchange</strong> <strong>2003 - 2013</strong> - <strong>install/admin</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Active Directory, Group Policy</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Good network troubleshooting skills</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Virtualisation experience</strong> - <strong>Vmware</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Routing and Switching - ideally Cisco</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>To meet the requirements of this role, you will have most of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ability to work in a team</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A robust sense of humour.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Results driven work ethic.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Connectwise and N-able/Labtech or similar experience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>I guess the key thing here is breadth of skills and a real keeness to excel in a Manged Services environment.&nbsp; So challenge me - hit me with your resumes people.. prove to me you have what it takes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Team @ Transparency</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="logo" src="https://www.seek.com.au/templates/25184377_1b_base.gif" /></p>\r\n', '', 'To meet the requirements of this role, you will have most of the following:\r\n\r\n    A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.\r\n    Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business\r\n    Ability to work in a team\r\n    Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.\r\n    A robust sense of humour.\r\n    Results driven work ethic.\r\n    Connectwise and N-able/Labtech or similar experience', 2, 1, 'Pert Northern Suburbs & Joondalup', '2017-07-27', 2, '', 1, '    Employee driven company culture\r\n    Great variety of work and opportunity to grow\r\n    Work hard, play hard team environment\r\n\r\nStrong desktop/server and customer service skillset? Able to troubleshoot complex problems? Worked for an IT company (MSP) doing support and projects?', '2016-12-01 19:20:24', '2016-12-01 19:20:24', 70000, 80000, 1, '$70k - $80k + super', 1, 0),
(8, 'AUO-2016-008', 20, 1, 2, 'Junior Mobile App Developer - Contract with view to Perm', '<p>Transparency&#39;s client is a WA based business, developing premium app&nbsp;solutions to for the medical industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They want an enthusiastic, entrepreneurial developer, to join their team full time.&nbsp;Someone with drive, someone dedicated to their craft, someone who likes to own their work and wants to build rock solid, enterprise class software, rather than settling for &quot;close enough&quot;. Someone who loves what they do and wants to build a a career around it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transparency&#39;s ideal candidate will have a suite of apps in IOS and Android they will have developed and be able to demo. While you may not have extenstive commercial experience you will enjoy developing in a structured enterprise type way with best practices implemented. You will have a proven track record designing and delivering cross platform mobile apps.&nbsp;You will be a swift learner and have done in-depth development&nbsp;work as well as back end coding and will want to take on a role where you can spread your&nbsp;wings and go deep in development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the Transparency candidate, you will have <strong>most</strong>, if not all of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Be an enthusiastic, inquisitive person</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be able to prove a genuine track record in development and have a strong history with Java and C++ and Objective-C</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Possess genuine abilities in IOS and Android Development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Have enterprise/commercial&nbsp;level development experience</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be expert in test driven development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be a confident and fluent communicator, speaking and writing excellent English (this one is a must, not a want)</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If this sounds like you, get in touch today and fling your CV through. Our eager CV readers are ready and waiting to peruse them and start interviewing the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have got this far and still don&#39;t think it&#39;s for you &ndash; follow us on twitter @transparencyit for the latest updates on jobs, candidate tips and just some generally funny stuff that we read on resumes from time to time!<br />\r\nThe Team at Transparency</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '    Be an enthusiastic, inquisitive person\r\n    Be able to prove a genuine track record in development and have a strong history with Java and C++ and Objective-C\r\n    Possess genuine abilities in IOS and Android Development\r\n    Have enterprise/commercial level development experience\r\n    Be expert in test driven development\r\n    Be a confident and fluent communicator, speaking and writing excellent English (this one is a must, not a want)', 2, 2, 'CBD, Inner & Western Suburbs', '2017-07-27', 2, '', 1, '    Fresh, youthful company\r\n    Great opportunity to deliver high quality products for the medical industry\r\n    Be a larger fish in a small pond - get valued for what you deliver\r\n\r\nFired up about dev? Developed some apps you can demo to us? Want to convert your skills to building great software commercially?', '2016-12-01 19:26:29', '2017-01-31 10:13:05', 500, 1000, 0, '1000', 1, 0),
(9, 'AUO-2016-009', 78, 1, 1, 'Support Engineer', '<p>Every so often a job comes along and I think to myself, mmm if this role was around when I was early in my IT career I&#39;d be mad not jump at it. And if I had where might I be now, other than in recruitment... ;-)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So if you want to avoid looking down the barrel of dead end jobs but instead want to progress your career in a dynamic, fresh IT company... you&#39;ll want to read on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This company culture is:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Dynamic, fresh, alive</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Staff are looked after and cared for in a team environment</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>The work is varied and challenging and employees are supported with training and development</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>So what&#39;s the catch? The catch is you have to prove you have the personality, soft skills and tenancity to make it in an MSP (multi client, time billing) environment. It takes a special someone to be able handle the rigours of MSP life, particularly if you haven&#39;t worked in one before.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ideal candidate would have a combination of soft skills and IT expertise to be able to deliver great customer service experience to the company&#39;s wide range of clients. Attention to detail, doing a job well, and being on top of your game technically are all essential attributes for this role. You will need to have outstanding customer service and communication skills, be able to work in a team and have solid, broad tech skills. The role will also involve being onsite in front of clients from time to time so professional presentation and a social easy going, friendly manner are absolutely essential.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Strong support experience with the following technologies are needed &ndash;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Desktops in AD environments</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Server 2003 - 2012</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Small Business Server 2003/2008/2011</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exchange</strong> <strong>2003 - 2013, O365 - admin/support</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Active Directory, GP, Microsoft SQL</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Hyper V, </strong><strong>Terminal Server</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Switches, Routers exposure</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In this role, you will get to make use of your great troubleshooting skills, combining this with a flair for communicating with non-technical clients. If you have a combination of solid desktop and server support skills blended with energetic customer service, apply now.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To meet the requirements of this role, you will have most of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ability to work in a team.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A broad skillset and up to date knowledge of infrastructure, comms and business systems/applications.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A robust sense of humour.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Results driven work ethic.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Contribute high quality documentation</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>MSP experience and knowledge in MSP tools (ConnectWise, ScreenConnect and LabTech) is highly desirable.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>OK, I know, I know we are asking for a lot. What&#39;s the key thing? Personality, Customer Service and the ability to learn fast. We can handle lower tech skills if we can see the potential to train them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So challenge me - hit me with your resumes people.. prove to me you have what it takes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Team @ Transparency</p>\r\n', '', '    A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.\r\n    Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business\r\n    Ability to work in a team.\r\n    A broad skillset and up to date knowledge of infrastructure, comms and business systems/applications.\r\n    Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.\r\n    A robust sense of humour.\r\n    Results driven work ethic.\r\n    Contribute high quality documentation\r\n    MSP experience and knowledge in MSP tools (ConnectWise, ScreenConnect and LabTech) is highly desirable.', 2, 2, 'Eastern Suburbs', '2017-07-27', 2, '', 1, '    Unique, switched on IT Company (MSP)\r\n    Challenging varied support role\r\n    Solid, stable company with a dynamic fresh attitude\r\n\r\nStrong desktop and server skillset? Able to troubleshoot complex problems? Worked for an IT company (MSP) doing support?', '2016-12-01 19:31:10', '2017-01-31 10:13:35', 45000, 60000, 1, '$45k - $60k + super + extras', 1, 0),
(10, 'AUO-2016-010', 78, 1, 1, 'Support Engineer', '<p>One of Transparency&#39;s IT solutions provider client is looking&nbsp;for a strong&nbsp;IT Support Technician to provide the best customer service experience to their customers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This company culture is:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Dynamic, fresh, alive</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Staff are looked after and cared for in a team environment</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>The work is varied and challenging and employees are supported with training and development</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The ideal candidate would have a combination of soft skills and IT expertise to be able to deliver great customer service experience to the company&#39;s wide range of clients. Attention to detail, doing a job well, and being on top of your game technically are all essential attributes for this role. You will need to have outstanding customer service and communication skills, be able to work in a team and have solid, broad tech skills. The role will also involve being onsite in front of clients from time to time so professional presentation and a social easy going, friendly manner are absolutely essential.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Strong support experience with the following technologies are needed &ndash;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Desktops in AD environments</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Windows Server 2003 - 2012</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Small Business Server 2003/2008/2011</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exchange</strong> <strong>2003 - 2013, O365 - admin/support</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Active Directory, GP, Microsoft SQL</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Hyper V, </strong><strong>Terminal Server</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Switches, Routers exposure</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In this role, you will get to make use of your great troubleshooting skills, combining this with a flair for communicating with non-technical clients. If you have a combination of solid desktop and server support skills blended with energetic customer service, apply now.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To meet the requirements of this role, you will have most of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ability to work in a team.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A broad skillset and up to date knowledge of infrastructure, comms and business systems/applications.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>A robust sense of humour.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Results driven work ethic.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Contribute high quality documentation</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>MSP experience and knowledge in MSP tools (ConnectWise, ScreenConnect and LabTech) is highly desirable.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>So challenge me - hit me with your resumes people.. prove to me you have what it takes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have got this far and still don&#39;t think it&#39;s for you &ndash; follow our blog transparencyitblog.com for the latest updates on jobs, candidate tips and just some generally interesting IT technical/funny stuff.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Team @ Transparency</p>\r\n', '', '    A warm yet professional phone manner with a genuine customer service focus.\r\n    Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business\r\n    Ability to work in a team.\r\n    A broad skillset and up to date knowledge of infrastructure, comms and business systems/applications.\r\n    Be rigorous in managing daily maintenance tasks.\r\n    A robust sense of humour.\r\n    Results driven work ethic.\r\n    Contribute high quality documentation\r\n    MSP experience and knowledge in MSP tools (ConnectWise, ScreenConnect and LabTech) is highly desirable.', 2, 2, 'Eastern Suburbs', '2017-07-27', 2, '', 1, '    Unique, switched on IT Company (MSP)\r\n    Challenging varied support role\r\n    Solid, stable company with a dynamic fresh attitude\r\n\r\nStrong desktop and server skillset? Able to troubleshoot complex problems? Worked for an IT company (MSP) doing support?', '2016-12-01 19:44:04', '2017-01-31 10:14:10', 45000, 54998, 0, '$45k - $55k + super + bonuses', 1, 0),
(11, 'AUO-2016-011', 48, 1, 1, 'IT Sales - office based role', '<p>Our client is a leading national reseller of IT products and solutions. They are looking for a great inbound IT Sales person&nbsp;to drive the sales of known brands to the education sector around WA.&nbsp; They have a great work environment, social and friendly team culture and a clear company focus and direction. It&#39;s easy to see where you fit and how you can make a difference in this company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You want this role because:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>With this household name behind you it is not difficult to open doors</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You love dealing with people and have heaps of energy</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>They attractively remunerate the right people</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You have a background in IT or the Education sector</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To meet the requirements of this role, you will have most of the following:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proven sales&nbsp;experience on IT products and solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Have a number of business contacts in Perth to help grow your sales base</li>\r\n	<li>A warm yet professional manner with a genuine trusted adviser manner.</li>\r\n	<li>Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work in a team</li>\r\n	<li><strong>A sales hungry manner</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Results driven work ethic</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Experience selling technical products and solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Self-motivated and goal driven</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This role is phone and office based, so you&#39;ll need to be adept at making calls and building relationships over the phone. They are looking for someone who is not just a farmer but a real hunter as well. You will work within the sales team selling to schools all over WA solving their problems with innovative IT products and solutions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sales hungry people who want the power of a big name to sell from&nbsp;should send their resumes to me... like now...&nbsp;:-)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Daniel Linden</p>\r\n', '', '    Proven sales experience on IT products and solutions\r\n    Have a number of business contacts in Perth to help grow your sales base\r\n    A warm yet professional manner with a genuine trusted adviser manner.\r\n    Outstanding interpersonal skills at all levels of business\r\n    Ability to work in a team\r\n    A sales hungry manner\r\n    Results driven work ethic\r\n    Experience selling technical products and solutions\r\n    Self-motivated and goal driven', 2, 2, 'Northern Suburbs & Joondalup', '2017-07-27', 1, '', 1, '    Sell IT products and services with the power of a big name that opens doors\r\n    Combine your IT knowledge with a massive product range to close big deals\r\n    Dynamic and fresh attitude to doing IT sales to the education sector\r\n\r\nAre you passionate about IT and sales? Great selling to a specific market over the phone? Apply today', '2016-12-01 19:50:02', '2017-01-31 10:14:41', 60000, 65000, 0, '$60k - $65k base + super + comms', 1, 0),
(12, 'AUO-2016-012', 20, 1, 3, 'Java Developer - Contract', '<h1>Java Developer - Contract</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Transparency&#39;s client is a WA based business, developing premium app&nbsp;solutions for various industries with this project being in the financial sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They want an enthusiastic Java Developer, to join their team on a contract basis for around 3 months.&nbsp;Someone with drive, someone dedicated to their craft, someone who likes to own their work and wants to build rock solid, enterprise class software, rather than settling for &quot;close enough&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transparency&#39;s ideal candidate will have spent at least 5&nbsp;years in the industry&nbsp;doing development work inside a structured environment.&nbsp;You will be a swift learner and have done in-depth development&nbsp;work as well as back end coding, front end framework exposure and will want to take on a role where you can spread your&nbsp;wings and go deep in development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the Transparency candidate, you will have <strong>most</strong>, if not all of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>5+ years Java experience dev experience (full stack)&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Knowledge of common Java frameworks eg Hibernate, Spring</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>TDD/ Agile methodologies</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Experience in the financial sector</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>JavaScript/Front end framework exposure</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>AWS or Azure experience</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Have enterprise/commercial&nbsp;level development experience</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be expert in test driven development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be a confident and fluent communicator, speaking and writing excellent English (this one is a must, not a want)</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If this sounds like you, get in touch today and fling your CV through. Our eager CV readers are ready and waiting to peruse them and start interviewing the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Team at Transparency</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="logo" src="https://www.seek.com.au/templates/25184377_1b_base.gif" /></p>\r\n', '', '\r\n    5+ years Java experience dev experience (full stack) \r\n    Knowledge of common Java frameworks eg Hibernate, Spring\r\n    TDD/ Agile methodologies\r\n    Experience in the financial sector\r\n    JavaScript/Front end framework exposure\r\n    AWS or Azure experience\r\n    Have enterprise/commercial level development experience\r\n    Be expert in test driven development\r\n    Be a confident and fluent communicator, speaking and writing excellent English (this one is a must, not a want)', 2, 2, 'CBD, Inner & Western Suburbs', '2017-07-27', 2, '', 1, '    Fresh, youthful company\r\n    Great opportunity to deliver high quality apps\r\n    Be a larger fish in a small pond - get valued for what you deliver\r\n\r\nFired up about dev? Proven senior development role record? Develop in an exciting company building great software', '2016-12-01 19:54:49', '2016-12-01 19:54:49', 500, 1000, 0, '1000', 1, 0),
